\id GLO - Sudest 
\h Utu Gharumwaru 
\toc1 VaŇča Vanat…®na Utu Gharumwaru 
\toc2 Utu Gharumwaru 
\toc3 Utugha 
\mt1 VaŇča Vanat…®na Utu Gharumwaru  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1  \k Abel\k* \it [English: Abel]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Mat 23:35; Luk 11:51; Hib 11:4; 12:24). Abel va ghaghae Kein na nasiyeniye. Hu thuwe \bd Kein\bd*.   
\p
\v 2  \k Ageit\k* \it [English: agate]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Vat 4:3; 21:11, 18-19). Ageit iye var…® thovuye lagh…®ye, na ma lemoyo inanjiwe. Hu thuwe \bd Var…® thovuthovuye na modanji lagh…®ye\bd*.   
\p
\v 3  \k Adam\k* \it [English: Adam]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Luk 3:38; Rom 5:12-15; 1Kor 15:22, 45-47; 1Tim 2:13-14; Jiud 14). Adam iye lolo Loi va i vakathakai. Loi va i wo yambaneke thelauniye na i vakathawe. Amba muyai i vakatha Ive. Hu thuwe \bd Ive\bd*.  
\pi1 Adam weiye levo, th…® raka Loi le mbaro na th…® vakatha thar…®. MbaŇčako iyako na i ghaoko, ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye mbe th…® vakavakatha vara thar…®.  
\pi1 1 Korinita e t…®ne, Pol i uno Jisas Krais iye Adam muyai. Adam i viva moli iye ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye rumbunji. Ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye th…® wo yawalinjiwe. Jisas Krais, iye Adam muyai moli, i giya yawal…® memeghanananiye weŇčgiya thavala th…® loŇčweghath…®we.   
\p
\v 4  \k Aisake\k* \it [English: Isaac]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Vak 7:8; Rom 9:7; Hib 11:9; na vavana). Aisake Eibraham na Sera narinji. Idake iyake gharumwaru ‚Äúvav…®r…®.‚ÄĚ Va th…® wogiya idake iyakewe, kaiwae Sera va i vav…®r…® mbaŇča i loŇčwekai Loi le dagerawe iya va iŇčake ne nanarun mbaŇča kaero u thanja. Hu thuwe \bd Eibraham\bd*.   
\p
\v 5  \k Aiseya\k* \it [English: Isaiah]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Mat 3:3; Vak 8:30; Rom 9:27-29; na vavana). Aiseya va Loi ghal…®ngae gharautu lagh…®ye moli. Va i vivako amba muyai Jisas i vir…®, Aiseya i utugiya bigibigi lemoyo Jisas kaiwae.   
\p
\v 6  \k Alabasita\k* \it [English: alabaster]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Mat 26:7; Mak 14:3; Luk 7:37). MbaŇča regha wevo regha i th…®mena bod…®la bunama butiye thovuye regha na i liŇčgi e vwatae. Bunamake iyake ina bod…®la th…® vakatha var…® regha idae alabasita.   
\p
\v 7  \k Alepa\k* \it [English: alpha]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Vat 1:8; 21:6; 22:13). Alepa iye leta i viva moli vaŇča Grik lenji alpabet e t…®ne, Ňčgoreiye ‚Äúa‚ÄĚ iye leta i viva vaŇča lumo alpabet e t…®ne. Iya kaiwae, mbaŇča va th…® rori Jisas iye Alepa, gharumwaru iye i viva moli, amba muyai bigi reghava.  
\pi1 Jisas tembe th…® unova Omega. Omega iye leta muyai moli vaŇča Grik lenji alpabet e t…®ne. Iya kaiwae va th…® rori Jisas iye Omega, gharumwaru iye ne muyai moli. Vatomwe 1:8, Jisas i dage ghamberegha kaiwae, iŇča, ‚ÄúGhino Alepa na Omega, ghino va e R…®ghendake na ne Eleghambakoko.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 8  \k Ametis\k* \it [English: amethyst]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Vat 4:3; 21:11, 18-19). Ametis iye var…® thovuye lagh…®ye, na ma lemoyo inanjiwe. Hu thuwe \bd Var…® thovuthovuye na modanji lagh…®ye\bd*.   
\p
\v 9  \k Ariyopagas\k* \it [English: Areopagus]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Vak 17:19, 34). Ariyapagas va bobokulu regha ina ghemba lagh…®ye idae Atens Gris e le val…®vaŇčga. Ghar…®ghar…®ko lagh…®lagh…®ye va th…® mevathavatha e bobokuluko iyako vwatae. Na Atens lenji kot lagh…®ye ghamba niva tembe th…® unova idae Ariyopagas.   
\p
\v 10  \k Atemis\k* \it [English: Artemis]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Vak 19:24-35). Atemis va loi kwankwan wevo eunda, iya ghar…®ghar…® inanji Eisiya e le val…®vaŇčga va th…® kururuwe.   
\p
\v 11  \k Baal\k* \it [English: Baal]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Rom 11:4). Baal iye loi kwankwan idae. Va i vivako, amba muyai Loi le ghar…®ghar…® th…® yaku Isirel e t…®ne, ghar…®ghar…®ko va th…® yaku gheko mbe th…® kurukururuwe Baal. MbaŇča Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® yakuwe, mbaŇča vavana th…® viyathu th…® kururuwe Loi iyameŇčge th…® kururuwe Baal. Iyake kaiwae Loi i gharegaith…® wanaŇčgi.   
\p
\v 12  \k Babilon\k* \it [English: Babylon]\it* ‚ÄĒ Babilon iye ghemba lagh…®ye va i vivako idae. KiŇčko i yaku gheko i kivwalaŇčgiya vanautuma lemoyo. Le ghar…®ghar…® th…® gaith…® weŇčgiya Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye na th…® kivwalaŇčgi. Th…® vaŇčguŇčgi lemoyo e lenji vanautuma na th…® tabona rakakaiwobwaga. Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye va th…® yakuyaku gheko theghathegha iyepir…®. (Mat 1:11-12, 17; Vak 7:43)  
\pi1 Vatomwe ghararori i utuŇča Babilon kaiwae gharayakuyaku ma th…® goruwe Loi. Vatomwe e t…®ne Babilon i meth…® ghembaghemba ma th…® goru weya Loi. Mbwata Babilon i meth…® Rom, o mbwata yambaneke ghambaro lagh…®ye. 1 Pita 5:13 e t…®ne, Babilon mbwata i meth…® Rom.   
\p
\v 13  \k Balaam\k* \it [English: Balaam]\it* ‚ÄĒ (2Pit 2:15; Jiud 11; Vat 2:14). Balaam va ghal…®Ňčae gharautu regha iya kiŇč regha idae Balak i naŇčgowe na i gura Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye. Va nuwaiya i vur…®gheghe kivwalaŇčgi. Balak, Mowab lenji kiŇč, iye i mararuŇča Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye mbaŇčaniye th…® yaku Mowas e t…®ne. Iviva Balaam i botewo na i gura Loi le ghar…®ghar…® o i wa Mowab, ko amba kaero i wa. E kamwath…® mborowa e t…®ne, nyao thovuye i ndegana kamwath…®ko, ko Balaam ma val…®kaiwae i thuwe, ko iyamaeŇčge doŇčkiko Balaam i thakowe i thuwe na i ndeghath…®, othembe Balaam i iŇčgeŇčgeŇča. Amba doŇčkiko i dagewe Balaam na i Ňčael…®mbiyawana. Balaam ma val…®kaiwae i guraŇčgiya Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye kaiwae Loi ghare weŇčgi. Buk Boboma Togha e t…®ne iŇča Balaam i gharethovu lagh…®ye weya mani, iya kaiwae i varaeŇča weiye Balak othembe Balak iye Loi le ghar…®ghar…® ghanjith…®g…®ya. (Legha 22‚Äď24).   
\p
\v 14  \k Bali\k* \it [English: barley]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Jon 6:9, 13; Vat 6:6). Bali iye mbombouye Ňčgoreiye wit. Ghar…®ghar…® th…® vakaiwoŇča mbombouye na th…® vakatha bred. Bred th…® vakatha weiye bali le thovuye seiwo ko bred th…® vakatha wit le thovuye lagh…®ye. MbaŇčaŇčgiko thiyako Jisas va ina e yambaneke, wit vwarara modae i lagh…®ye kivala bali vwarara modae.   
\p
\v 15  \k Bap…®taiso\k* \it [English: baptism]\it* ‚ÄĒ Buk Boboma e t…®ne th…® rori Jon Rabap…®taiso va i bap…®taisoŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® lemoyo e Walagh…®ta Jordan e t…®ne. Va i dage weŇčgi wo th…® uturaŇčgiya lenji thar…® na th…® roiteteŇčgi ambane i bap…®taisoŇčgi. Bap…®taisoke iyake le r…®ghe na ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye th…® ghareghare ghar…®ghar…®ko thiyako va th…® uturaŇčgiya lenji thar…® na th…® roiteteŇčgi. E kamwath…®ke iyake Jon i vivathaŇčgi ghar…®ghar…® e gharenji Jisas le mena kaiwae.  
\pi1 MbaŇča lolo regha i loŇčweghath…® Jisas Krais, nuwaiya i bap…®taiso na mbala ghar…®ghar…® th…® thuwe i tabona Kristiyan.  
\pi1 Bap…®taiso gharumwaru iyake. Loloke i bap…®taiso iye va i uturaŇčgiya le thar…® na i roteteŇčgi. I varum…®nje Jisas Krais, iya i dagerawe na i numotena lenji thar…® thavala th…® var…®minje. Na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva nuwaiya i ghambu Jisas Krais.   
\p
\v 16  \k Benjamin\k* \it [English: Benjamin]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Vak 13:21; Rom 11:1; Pilip 3:5; Vat 7:8). Benjamin va Jakob le ŇčgamaŇčgamaŇčgi theyaworo na theghewo regha na iye nasiyeninji. Iya kaiwae uu theyaworo na theghewo regha, iye va rumbuye. Hu thuwe \bd Eibraham\bd*.   
\p
\v 17  \k Beril\k* \it [English: beryl]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Vat 4:3; 21:11, 18-19). Beril iye var…® thovuye lagh…®ye, na ma lemoyo inanjiwe. Hu thuwe \bd Var…® thovuthovuye na modanji lagh…®ye\bd*.   
\p
\v 18  \k Bil…®sabul\k* \it [English: Beelzebul]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Mat 10:25; 12:24, 27; Mak 3:22; Luk 11:15, 18-19). Bil…®sabul iye nyao raraithar…® ghanjigiya idae. Idake iyake i mena weya ida regha, Baal-zebub, nyaoŇčgiko regha iya thiye uko vavana inanji Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye ghadidinji va th…® kurukururuwe. Nyaoko raraithar…® ghanjigiya idae Seitan. Hu thuwe \bd Satan\bd*.   
\p
\v 19  \k Bred ma weiye is…®t\k* Hu thuwe \bd Bred Ma Weiye Is…®t Gha Thaga, Thaga e t…®ne\bd*.   
\p
\v 20  \k Dagerawe\k* \it [English: Promise/Covenant]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Dagerawe Teuye: Luk 1:72; Vak 3:25; 7:8; Gal 3:17; Hibru 9:1. Dagerawe Togha: Mat 26:28; Mak 14:24; Luk 22:20; Rom 11:27; 1Kor 11:25; 2Kor 3:14; Hibru 7:22; 8:6-13; 9:15; 10:16, 29; 12:24; 13:20). Dagerawe iya ghar…®ghar…® theghewo or wabwi theghewo th…® vevaraeŇča weŇčgi. Dagerawe e t…®ne, lolo regha o wabwi regha i dagerawe na th…® vakatha bigi regha kaiwae, na iye wone i vakatha big regha. Loi le dagerawe e t…®ne, iye Loi va i dagerawe weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®, iŇča ne Ramanji na ghanji Giya. Ghar…®ghar…®ko wone th…® ghambu.  
\pi1 Dagerawe theghewo Loi va i vakatha weiyaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®. Dagerawe Teuye na Dagerawe Togha. Dagerawe Teuye iye Loi va i wogiya e ou Sainai. Loi va i dagerawe ne i njimbukikiya ghar…®ghar…® na le ghar…®ghar…® thoŇčgo thiye th…® ghambugha vara Mosese le Mbaroko wolagh…®ye. Ko iyemaeŇčge ma val…®kaiwae lolo regha i ghambuvao Mosese le Mbaroko wolagh…®ye, iya kaiwae ma lolo regha val…®kaiwae Loi i wovarumwarumwaruŇča Dagerawe Teuye ghambaŇča e t…®ne.  
\pi1 Dagerawe Togha e t…®ne Loi i dagerawe thoŇčgo lolo regha i loŇčweghath…® Jisas Krais, ne i wovarumwarumwaruŇča. Val…®kaiwae i vakatha iyake kaiwae mbaŇča Jisas i mare, i wo Loi le lith…® ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye lenji thar…® kaiwae. Iya kaiwae thela thoŇčgo i loŇčweghath…® Jisas Krais i tabona i rumwaru, Ňčgoreiye ma mbaŇča regha i vakatha thar…® o i raka Loi le mbaro mbe regha eŇčge.   
\p
\v 21  \k Dagerawe gha Bogis\k* \it [English: Ark of the Covenant]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Hib 9:4; Vat 11:19). Bogiske iyake va bogis th…® vakatha e umbwa (timba). Vwataeko va th…® monje vagh…®liya e gol. E t…®ne var…® lagh…®ye theghewo inanjiwe, iya va Loi i rori le mbaro theyaworomawe. Lenji gh…®nagha e t…®nenji ghar…®ghar…®ko va th…® bigiya bogiske iyake. MbaŇča th…® yakuyaku, th…® th…®nruwo bogiske iyake Mevathavatha Ňägoloniye e t…®ne moli. Bogiske iyake na bigibigiko inanji e t…®neko th…® boboma lagh…®ye kaiwae thiye Loi le nono weŇčgiya Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye le dagerawe kaiwanji. Va th…® vakatha Ňägolo Boboma e ghereiye, bogiske i yakuyaku e t…®ne, ina Woluwolu Bobomako Moli e t…®ne.   
\p
\v 22  \k Deivid\k* \it [English: David]\it* ‚ÄĒ Deivid iye va kiŇč lagh…®ye regha Isirel e t…®ne. Iye Jese nariye taboghaniye vara. Amba va th…® vakathana kiŇč o giya, va mbowo i njimbukikiya ramae le sip. Va mbaŇča regha mbaŇča vamba tabogha, va i gaith…® weiye ragagaith…® lagh…®ye moli regha na i tagavamare.  
\pi1 Deivid i gharethovu lagh…®ye moli weya Loi. Va i roriya wothuwothu lemoyo moli, Loi ghatarawa kaiwae, iye th…®Ňčana Sam.  
\pi1 Jisas iye Deivid rumbuye regha (Rom 1:3; Vat 22:16). MbaŇča mava Jisas i vir…®, Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautuŇčgi va th…® rori iye Krais na Ravamoru, iye Loi ne i variye, na i tabona Deivid rumbuye regha.   
\p
\v 23  \k Eibraham\k* \it [English: Abraham]\it* ‚ÄĒ Eibraham iye Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye rumbunji iviva moli. Va i vivako Loi i dagewe Eibraham ne i giyawe vanautuma togha. Eibraham na orumburumbuye lemoyo ne th…® yaku gheko na ghambanji. Loi va i dagewe na i iteta vanautuma iya va inakowe, na mbala i wa vetamweya vanautumake togha iyake. Eibraham va i ghambu Loi ghal…®Ňčae. Va i gh…®nagha bwagabwaga moli na i wo theghathegha molao moli. Vanautumako iyako mbaŇčake th…® uno idae Isirel.  
\pi1 Loi va i vakatha dagerawe weiye Eibraham, i dagerawe iye na orumburumbuye ne th…® tabona le ghar…®ghar…®. Ne i njimbukiki weŇčgi thoŇčgo th…® ghambu ghal…®Ňčae.  
\pi1 Eibraham levo idae Sera. Mava th…® ghamb…® ghaghada th…® thanja moli. Amba Loi i vakatha vakatha ghamba rotaele kaiwanji na Sera i ghamb…® nariye. Th…® rena idae Aisak.  
\pi1 MbaŇča Aisak i tabovoro lagh…®ye i ghe weiye Rebeka. Rebeka va i ghamb…® lenji ŇčgamaŇčgama theghewo, Ňčgama ruworuwo, idanji Iso na Jakob. MbaŇča th…® yakuyaku Loi i giya Jacob ida togha, Isirel. Jacob orumburumbuye thiye Jiu, na th…® uno idanji regha Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye.  
\pi1 Jakob va i mbuwawoŇčaŇčgi theunyiwo, idanji Liya na Rachel. Tembe Ňčgoreiyeva i ghe weiye rakakaiwobwaga euniwo. Jakob leŇčgaŇčga Ruben, Simiyon, Livai, Juda, Isakar, Sebulon, Gad, Asir, Josep, Benjamin, Dan na Napatali. Theyaworo na theghewoko thiyako lenji gamagai va ighanagha moli, na thiye lenji gamagai tembe Ňčgoreiyeva ighanagha moli. Taulagh…®ko thiye Isirel orumbrumbuye, na iye Eibraham rumbuye.   
\p
\v 24  \k Emerold\k* \it [English: Emerald]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Vat 4:3; 21:19). Emerold iye var…® ghayamoyamo thovuye moli na ma lemoyo inanji. Hu thuwe \bd Var…® thovuthovuye na modanji lagh…®ye\bd*.   
\p
\v 25  \k Eron\k* \it [English: Aaron]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Luk 1:5; Vak 7:40; Hib 5:4; 7:11; 9:4). Eron rumbuye Livai iyava Jakob le ŇčgamaŇčgama theyaworo na theghewo regha. Eron va ravowovowo i viva moli. Loi va iŇča ravowovowo wolagh…®ye ne th…® mena Eron orumburumbuye weŇčgi.  
\pi1 Eron ghaghae Mosese, na iye lagh…®yeniye. Raiwo na ghaghaeke va th…® vir…® mbaŇča Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye va th…® yaku Ijipt e t…®ne na th…® tabona rakakaiwobwaga. Eron va i thalavu Mosese na th…® vaŇčguŇčgiya Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye na th…® voraŇčgi Ijipt.  
\pi1 Va mbaŇča regha ghar…®ghar…® vavana th…® th…®gh…®yawanaŇčgiya Mosese na Eron, Loi i vamanjamanjalaŇča wagiyawe thenjighewoko thiye randevivaŇčgi va i tuthi weŇčgiya Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye kaiwanji. Uu theyaworo na theghewo lenji randeviva regha na regha th…® wo umbwa iya i vatomwe iye ghauu lenji randeviva. Loi va i dage weŇčgiya Mosese na Eron na th…® bigivathavatha umbwa (umbwake thiyake uu lenji randeviva ghanjinono) na th…® bigiraweŇčgi Mevathavatha Ňägoloniye e t…®ne. Loi va iŇča loloko va i tuthiko le umbwa ne i thalavwara. MbaŇča …®gh…®viyava, Eron le umbwa va i thalavwara, na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva i vunyenyeune na i rau na e uneune. Loi va iŇča Eron le umbwa val…®kaiwae ina Dagerawe gha Bogis e t…®ne iya ina Mevathavatha Ňägoloniye. Eron le umbwako va Loi ghanono weŇčgi. (Legha 17:1-10; Hib 9:4). Hu thuwe \bd Livai\bd* na \bd Mosese\bd*. Tembe hu thuweva \bd Dagerawe gha Bogis\bd*.   
\p
\v 26  \k Fig\k* \it [English: fig]\it* ‚ÄĒ Fig iye umbwa regha na i rau na une th…® loghe moli.   
\p
\v 27  \k Ghal…®Ňčae gharaghamb…®\k* \it [English: apostle]\it* ‚ÄĒ Jisas va i tuthiya gharaghambu theyaworo na theghewo na thiye ghal…®Ňčae gharaghamb…® (Mat 10:1-4; Mak 3:13-19; Luk 6:12-16). Amaamalake thiyake vambe th…® yakuvara weinji na i vavaghareŇčgi. Mbe e maranji vara va th…® thuwe le mare na le thuweiru. Jisas i variyeŇčgi na veth…® utuŇčga weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® budakaiya va th…® thuwe na veth…® vavaghareŇča Totoniye Thovuye weŇčgi. Thiye va th…® tabona Jisas gharaloŇčweloŇčweghath…® ghanjigiyagiya.  
\pi1 MbaŇča muyai Jisas i yomarawe Pol na i tuthiva na ghal…®Ňčae gharaghamb…®. Banabas na ghar…®ghar…®ko seiwova th…® uno ghal…®Ňčae gharaghamb…®, ko iyemaeŇčge Jisas mava i tuthiŇčgi.   
\p
\v 28  \k Ghamba vowo\k* \it [English: altar]\it* ‚ÄĒ Jiu vambe th…® vowovowo vara weya Loi. Va th…® gabo thetheghan regha Ňčgoreiye sip, gout o burumwaka gh…®moru, na lenji vowo. Ghamba vowo, iyava th…® vakatha var…®, iya aŇčga th…® vowowe.  
\pi1 Va iri Moses ghambaŇča na i ghaoko, mbe ravowovowo eŇčge th…® vakatha vowo. Na va th…® vakatha mbe ghamba vowo eŇčge Mevathavatha Ňägoloniye e t…®ne, na muyai th…® vakatha Ňägolo Boboma e t…®ne. Ghamba vowo ina Ňägolo Boboma e t…®ne va Ňčgoreiye tebol lagh…®ye th…® vakatha brass. Tebol nasiye regha va ina gheko, th…® vakatha e gol. E vwatae ravowovowo th…® ngambu bigi butiye thovuye.   
\p
\v 29  \k Gharaghambu\k* \it [English: disciple]\it* ‚ÄĒ Ghar…®ghar…®ko, thiye th…® var…®minje Jisas, thiye th…® loŇčgweghath…® le utuutu na th…® ghambu, thiyeke ra uno gharaghambu. Buk Boboma Togha Vakatha e t…®ne, Jisas gharaghambuŇčgiko tene th…® unova ‚Äúthiye th…® longweghath…® Jisas‚ÄĚ na ‚ÄúoghaghaŇčguŇčgi.‚ÄĚ  
\pi1 Buk Boboma Togha Matiu, Mak, Luk na Jon e t…®nenji mbaŇčaviye th…® utuŇča Jisas gharaghambu thegheyaworo na theghewo. Gharaghambuko wolagh…®ye e t…®ne, Jisas va i tuthi theyaworo na theghewo na th…® yaku weinji. Tembe th…® unoŇčgiva Jisas ghal…®Ňčae gharaghamb…®Ňčgi (Mat 10:1-4). Hu thuwe \bd Ghal…®Ňčae Gharaghamb…®\bd*.   
\p
\v 30  \k Gidiyon\k* \it [English: Gideon]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Hib 11:32). Gidiyon va Isirel lenji randeviva regha. Iye va le loŇčweghath…® i lagh…®ye na i naŇčgo weya Loi na i njimbukikiŇčgi. MbaŇča i vaŇčguŇčgiya ragagaith…® na i viva weŇčgi gaith…® kaiwae, othembe ma taulagh…®Ňčgi iye e le val…®vaŇčgako, ko iyemaeŇčge thiye ne th…® kivwalaŇčgiya ghagh…®th…®yaŇčgiko kaiwae Loi i thalavuŇčgi.   
\p
\v 31  \k Gomora\k* \it [English: Gomorah]\it* ‚ÄĒ Hu thuwe \bd Sodoma\bd*.   
\p
\v 32  \k Grik, vaŇča Grik\k* \it [English: Greek, Greek language]\it* ‚ÄĒ Hu thuwe yambaneke ghamap na gheko hu thuwe vanautuma regha idae Grik. Atens na Korinita va ghembaghemba lagh…®lagh…®ye inanji Grik e t…®ne. Va i vivako Grik ghar…®ghar…®niye va thiya vavaona wagiyawe, na ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye th…® yavwatata wanaŇčgi lenji thimba kaiwae. VaŇča Grik ghar…®ghar…® ighanagha th…® vaŇča Grik e t…®ne, na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva iyaŇčganiye Grik ghanjiragagaith…® va th…® wa. Amaamala va th…® rori Buk Boboma Togha va th…® rori e vaŇča Grik.   
\p
\v 33  \k Heiga\k* \it [English: Hagar]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Gal 4:21-31). Heiga iye rakakaiwobwaga wevoniye Sera e le Ňčgolo t…®ne, Eibraham levo. E mbaŇčako iyako Sera ma vamba i ghamb…® Ňčgama, Sera i dage weya Eibraham na i ghena weiye Heiga, na Heiga i ghamb…® Ňčgama idae Ishmael. Ko Ishmael mava Ňčgama Loi va i dageraweya Eibraham, na Ishmael orumburumbuye mava th…® wo budakai Loi va i dagerawe na i wogiyawe Eibraham orumburumbuye. Amba Sera i ghamb…® Ňčgama. Eibraham i uno idae Aisake. Iye Loi le dagerawe Ňčgamaniye.  
\pi1 Amba Sera i ghamb…® Aisake e ghereiye, amba i gaith…®wana Heiga na i vakatha na i variyeyathu. Heiga i wa na ve yaku ou regha idae Sainai. Ina e ouko iyako theghathegha ighanagha, amba Loi i dage weya Mosese na i wogiya weya le mbaro. Iya kaiwae iŇča ina Galeisiya 4 Heiga, iya rakakaiwobwaga wevoniye, i meth…® Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye. Thiye Ňčgoranjiya rakakaiwobwaga weya Loi kaiwae th…® loŇčweghath…® thoŇčgo lolo i ghambuŇčgi le mbaro, iye Loi ne i wovatha na iŇčawe lolo rumwaru. Ma th…® loŇčweghath…® Loi ghal…®Ňčae iya ma th…® wovatha iye th…® rumwaru thavala th…® loŇčweghath…® Jisas Krais.   
\p
\v 34  \k Herod\k* \it [English: Herod]\it* ‚ÄĒ Buk Boboma Togha e t…®ne gh…®mogh…®moru theghevar…® th…® uno idanji Herod.  
\li1 1. KiŇč Herod, iya th…® uno ‚ÄúHerod i lagh…®ye moli,‚ÄĚ va Judiya lenji kiŇč mbaŇčaniye Jisas le vir…®. Iye va i mando na i vakatha Jisas i mare mbaŇča amba Ňčgama (Mat 2:1-22; Luk 1:5).  
\li1 2. Herod Antipas va Galili gharambarombaro mbaŇčaniye Jisas vs i vavaghare na i vakatha vakatha ghamba rotaele. Iye i vaŇčgu Herodiyas na i dage vur…®gheghe na th…® kitena Jon numwe. Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® yovaŇčgu Jisas we na i kot weiye, amba muyai th…® rokros. (Mak 6:14-29; Luk 23:6-12).  
\li1 3. KiŇč Herod Agripa Iye Iviva va i vakatha vuyowo lagh…®ye weŇčgiya thavala th…® loŇčweghath…® Jisas Krais e ekelesiya va i vivako e t…®ne. Va i tagavamare Jemes iye Jon ghaghae (Vak 12:1-23).  
\li1 4. KiŇč Herod Agripa Iye Theghewoniye iya Pol va i utugiya gha vuyowo amba muyai Gawana Pestas i variye Pol na i wa Rom na vekot Sisa e marae (Vak 25:13‚Äď26:2; 26:19, 27-32).   
\p
\v 35  \k Hibru\k* \it [English: Hebrew]\it* ‚ÄĒ Idake ‚ÄúHibru‚ÄĚ mboromboro weiye idae ‚ÄúJiu.‚ÄĚ Jiu o Hibru, thiye Eibraham orumburumbuŇčgi. Idake ‚ÄúHibru‚ÄĚ i mena weya lenji tanakau regha idae Eiba. Hu thuwe \bd Jiu\bd*.   
\p
\v 36  \k Hisop\k* \it [English: Hyssop]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Jon 19:29; Hib 9:19). Hisop iye umbwa regha. Ravowovowo va i li hisop yaŇčgae weiye ndamwandamwa na i vighath…® e mbothiye na i liutu e madibe amba i variriya ghar…®ghar…®ko o bigibigiko mbala th…® boboma Loi e marae.   
\p
\v 37  \k Hosana\k* \it [English: Hosana]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Mat 21:9, 15; Mak 11:9-10; Jon 12:13). ‚ÄúHosana‚ÄĚ iye dage mwaewo regha iya ghar…®ghar…® va th…® kula na th…® yavwatatawana lolo regha. Mbwata gharumwaru ‚ÄúLoi i vamoru‚ÄĚ o ‚ÄúRa tarawe.‚ÄĚ Ko Jisas ghambaŇča e t…®ne gharumwaru ‚ÄúRa taraweŇčge!‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 38  \k Ijipt\k* \it [English: Egypt]\it* ‚ÄĒ Ijipt iye vanautuma regha ina Isirel ghadidiye. Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye va thiye rakakaiwobwaga Ijipt e t…®ne theghathegha thegheseriyevar…® (Vak 7:34-38). Hu thuwe Rom Ghaghambambaro ghamap.   
\p
\v 39  \k Ilaija\k* \it [English: Elijah]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Mak 9:4; Rom 11:2-5; Jem 5:17; na vavana). Ilaija va Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu lagh…®ye, iya i Ňčaebar…®r…® wanaŇčgiya kiŇč raithar…® na taulagh…®ko thiyako th…® kururu weŇčgiya loi kwankwan Isirel e t…®ne. Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye lemoyo th…® renuwaŇča ne i njogha na i vanamwe kamwath…® Mesaiya le mena kaiwae. Jon Rabap…®taiso va Ňčgoreiye Ilaija kamwath…® lemoyo e t…®ne (Mat 11:14; Luk 1:17).   
\p
\v 40  \k Ilaisa\k* \it [English: Elisha]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Luk 4:27). Hu thuwe \bd Naaman\bd*.   
\p
\v 41  \k Inisen…®s\k* \it [English: Incense]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Luk 1:9-11; Vat 5:8; 8:3-4; 18:13). Inisen…®s butiye thovuye moli. Va th…® vakatha e umbwaumbwa thinji o ndamwandamwa na wathewatheliliye. Ňägolo Boboma e t…®ne th…® Ňčambu na butiye i thovuye mbaŇča ghar…®ghar…® va th…® naŇčgonaŇčgo weya Loi.   
\p
\v 42  \k Is…®t\k* \it [English: Yeast]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Mat 13:33; 16:12; 1Kor 5:6-8; Gal 5:9; na vavana). Is…®t th…® vakaiwoŇča na th…® vakatha bred. Iye i vakatha bred na i roro. Is…®t mbe nasiye eŇčge ne i vakatha bred lemoyo moli.   
\p
\v 43  \k Iso\k* \it [English: Esau]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Rom 9:10-13; Hib 11:20; 12:16-17). Eibraham nariye Aisake na levo Rebeka th…® ghamb…®Ňčgi gamwaruworuwo, Iso i vir…®viva na ghaghae Jeikob i vir…®reghamba. MbaŇča regha mbaŇča Iso bada i ghar…®, va i vakuneŇča budakai ne i wo kaiwae iye Aisake nariye i vir…®viva weya ghaghae Jeikob na modae ghan…®Ňčga regha wit th…® ge. Iya kaiwae va Jeikob orumburumbuye th…® tabona Loi le tututhi ghar…®ghar…®niye, ma Iso orumburumbuye. Hu thuwe \bd Eibraham\bd*.   
\p
\v 44  \k Isirel\k* \it [English: Isirel]\it* ‚ÄĒ Isirel iye mbe ida lagh…®ye Loi i wogiyawe Jeikob, Aisake na levo Rebeka narinji theghewo regha. Isirel le ŇčgamaŇčgama theyaworo na theghewo. Thiye va th…® tabona uu theyaworo na theghewo Isirel e t…®ne. Hu thuwe \bd Eibraham\bd*.  
\pi1 Isirel orumburumbuyeŇčgi idanji tomethi. Iviva th…® uno ‚ÄúIsirel le ghar…®ghar…®‚ÄĚ na muyai th…® uno ‚ÄúJiu ghar…®ghar…®niye.‚ÄĚ Tembe Ňčgoreiyeva th…® uno ‚ÄúHibru ghar…®ghar…®niye.‚ÄĚ Hu thuwe \bd Jiu\bd*.  
\pi1 Vanautumako iya Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye thiya yakukowe mbowo th…® unova Isirel. Va i vivako th…® uno Keinan. Ida regha iye Palastain.   
\p
\v 45  \k Ive\k* \it [English: Eve]\it* ‚ÄĒ (2Kor 11:3; 1Tim 2:13-14). Ive va Adam levo. Va e mbaŇčako iyako Loi va i vakatha yambaneke, va i vakathakai Adam. Amba i wo Adam ŇčgaŇčgaye na i vakatha Ive. Amba muyai Seitan i mena weya Ive na i valoghe nuwe na i ghan umbwako une iyava Loi i dageten na tha th…® ghan. Na tembe i wogiyava umbwama une na Adam i ghan. MbaŇčako iyako Adam na Ive th…® loŇčweyathu Loi ghal…®Ňčae, ghar…®ghar…® th…® vakatha thar…®. Kein, Abel na Set va Adam na Ive lenji ŇčgaŇčgaŇčgi.   
\p
\v 46  \k Jasinit\k* \it [English: jacinthe]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Vat 4:3; 21:11, 18-19). Jasinit iye var…® thovuye lagh…®ye, na ma lemoyo inanjiwe. Hu thuwe \bd Var…® thovuthovuye na modanji lagh…®ye\bd*.   
\p
\v 47  \k Jaspa\k* \it [English: jasper]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Vat 4:3; 21:11, 18-19). Jaspa iye var…® thovuye lagh…®ye, na ma lemoyo inanjiwe. Hu thuwe \bd Var…® thovuthovuye na modanji lagh…®ye\bd*.   
\p
\v 48  \k Jeikob\k* \it [English: Jacob]\it* ‚ÄĒ Jeikob va Aisake nariye. T…®nae Rebeka. Ghaghae gamwaruwo Iso. Othembe Iso i vir…®viva, Jeikob iye Loi va i tuthi na i lagh…®ye, Ňčgoreiye va i vir…®viva. Jeikob orumburumbuye Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye. Hu thuwe \bd Isirel\bd*, \bd Eibraham\bd*, na \bd Iso\bd*.   
\p
\v 49  \k Jeremaiya\k* \it [English: Jeremiah]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Mat 2:17; 16:14; 27:9). Jeremaiya va Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu. Va mbaŇčaniye mbaŇča Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye ma th…® ghambu Loi ghal…®Ňčae, Jeremaiya i dage weŇčgi na th…® uturaŇčgiya lenji thar…® na th…® roiteteŇčgi. Iye mbowo i utuŇčava bigibigi lemoyo ne th…® yomara Krais le mena ghambaŇča e t…®ne.   
\p
\v 50  \k Jese\k* \it [English: Jesse]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Mat 1:5-6; Luk 3:32; Vak 13:22; Rom 15:12). Jese nariye KiŇč Deivid, iye Jisas Krais rumbuye. Buk Boboma Teuye e t…®ne Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu Aiseya va iŇča Krais ne iye Jese na Deivid rumbunji. Hu thuwe \bd Deivid\bd*.   
\p
\v 51  \k Jisas\k* \it [English: Jesus]\it* ‚ÄĒ Idake iyake gharumwaru ‚ÄúRavamoru‚ÄĚ o ‚ÄúLa Loi iye ghanda Ravamoru.‚ÄĚ Meri nariye Loi va i rena idake iyake kaiwae Jisas ne i vamoruŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® e lenji thar…® t…®ne (Mat 1:21). Ida vavana th…® uno Jisas: Jisas Krais, Loi Nariye, Lolo Nariye na Deivid Nariye.   
\p
\v 52  \k Jiu\k* \it [English: Jew]\it* ‚ÄĒ Jiu thiye Eibraham orumburumbuye. Hu thuwe \bd Eibraham\bd*. MbaŇča va i vivako Jiu gharumwaru ‚Äúghar…®ghar…® thiya yaku Judiya e le val…®vaŇčga‚ÄĚ o ‚Äúghar…®ghar…® th…® mena uu Juda.‚ÄĚ Juda va Isirel ghanjiuu theyaworo na theghewo regha. Amba muyai Jiu gharumwaru ‚ÄúIsirel ghar…®ghar…®niyeko wolagh…®ye.‚ÄĚ Hu thuwe \bd Isirel\bd*.  
\pi1 Toto Thovuye Jon le rorori e t…®ne, utuke Jiu i meth…® Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye lenji randevivaŇčgi na lenji rambarombaro thiye th…® th…®gh…®yawana Jisas.   
\p
\v 53  \k Jiu lenji kot lagh…®ye\k* \it [English: Sanhedrin]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Mat 26:59; Mak 14:55; 15:1; Luk 22:66; Jon 11:47; Vak 4:15; 5:21; 6:12; 22:30; 23:1; 24:20). Sanhidren va kot lagh…®ye weiye Jiu amaamala thegheyepir…® na regha na e vwataeva. Amaamala thiye idaidanji lagh…®lagh…®ye. Kot…®ke iyake th…® tuthi bigibigi kururu kaiwanji. Rovowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye lenji randeviva i mbaronga lenji niva. MbaŇča th…® vangumena Jisas e marae, th…®Ňča ne i mare. Ko iyemaeŇče mbe Rom gharambarombaro eŇčge th…® tuthi na i mare, iya kaiwae va th…® variye na i wawe Pailat, Rom ghagawana regha.   
\p
\v 54  \k Jon\k* \it [English: Jon]\it* ‚ÄĒ Buk Boboma Togha lenji rarorori th…® utuŇča ghar…®ghar…® lemoyo idanji Jon. Theghewoko lagh…®ye moliko thiye Jon Rabap…®taiso na Jon iye Jisas ghal…®Ňčae gharaghamb…® regha:  
\li1 1. Jon Rabap…®taiso ‚ÄúJon the Baptizer‚ÄĚ va Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu regha i vivatharawe kamwath…® Jisas kaiwae. Iye ghal…®Ňčae gharautu va Ňčgoreiye Ilaija, na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva Ilaija, i dage vur…®gheghe weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® na th…® uturaŇčgiya lenji thar…® na th…® roiteteŇčgi mbala Loi ne i numotenŇčgi. Hu thuwe Mat 3:1-15; 11:2-19; 14:1-12; 17:13; 21:24-32; Mak 1:4-11; 6:14-29; 11:29-33; Luk 1:13-17, 57-63, 76-80; 3:2-20; 7:18-33; 11:1; Jon 1:6-8,15, 19-36; 3:22-30.  
\li1 2. Jon Jisas ghal…®Ňčgae gharaghamb…® regha ‚ÄúJon the Apostle‚ÄĚ va Sebedi nariye na Jemes ghaghae. Va i rori Toto Thovuye Jisas Krais, Jon Le Roriri, na Leta Iviva, Theghewoniye na Theghetoniye Jon Le Rorori, na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva Vatomwe. Hu thuwe Mat 4:21-22; 10:2; 17:1-13; Mak 1:29; 3:17; 5:37; 9:1-13, 38; 10:35-41; 13:3; Luk 8:51; 9:28-36,49,54; 22:8; Vak 3:1-11; 4:13, 19-20; 8:14-17; Gal 2:9; Vat 1:1,4,9; 22:2,8.  
\pi1 Vavana tembe idanjiva Jon:  
\li1 3. Jon Mak, iye Banabas ighaiye na Pol le val…®rakakaiwo, i roriya Toto Thovuye Mak Le Rorori. Hu thuwe Vak 12:12; 13:4-13; 15:37-39; Kol 4:10; 2Tim 4:11; Pilim 24; 1Pit 5:13.  
\li1 4. Saimon Pita ramae va idae Jon (Mat 16:17; Jon 1:42; 21:15-17).  
\li1 5. Ravowovowo lagh…®ye Anas le boda regha idae Jon (Vak 4:6).   
\p
\v 55  \k Jona\k* \it [English: Jonah]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Mat 12:39-41; 16:4; Luk 11:29-32). Jona va Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu regha. MbaŇča regha Loi i variye na i wa e ghemba idae Ninive na i vavaghare Loi totoniye weŇčgi. Ko iyemaeŇčge ma nuwaiya i ghambu Loi. I tha e waŇčga regha na i wava e ghawo reghava. MbaŇča vambe ina e waŇčga, Loi i variye ndewendewe lagh…®yewe. Ghar…®ghar…®ko inanji waŇčgako th…® gharegharekai Loi i gharegaith…®we Jona na iyake kaiwae i rowo lagh…®ye. Iya kaiwae th…® wokiyathu e njigh…®jko t…®ne na th…® vamoruŇčgi ghanjimberegha. Borogi lagh…®ye va i kovululu Jona, na i yaku e Ňčgamoiye mbaŇča mbaŇčato amba borogiko i thegharaŇčgiya e kerakera vwatae. Iyake e ghereiye, Jona i ghambu Loi na i wa Ninive na i vavaghare Loi totoniye gheko.   
\p
\v 56  \k Josep\k* \it [English: Joseph]\it* ‚ÄĒ Ghar…®ghar…® tomethi inanji Buk Boboma Togha e t…®ne idanjiya Josep.  
\li1 1. Jakob le ŇčgamaŇčgama theyaworo na theghewo, thiye Isirel orumburumbunji, regha idae Josep. Iye ghaghae moli Benjamin. Hu thuwe Vak 7:9-14; Jon 4:5; Hib 11:21-22; Vat 7:8.  
\li1 2. Josep, iye Meri Jisas t…®nae le gh…®moru. Hu thuwe Mat 1:16, 18-20, 24; 2:13, 19; Luk 1:27; 2:4, 16, 33, 43; 3:23; 4:22; Jon 1:45; 6:42.  
\li1 3. Josep, Jisas ghaghae regha. Hu thuwe Mat 13:55; Mak 6:42.  
\li1 4. Josep, Jemes iye th…® uno taboghaniye ghaghae. Hu thuwe Mat 27:56; Mak 15:40, 47.  
\li1 5. Josep iye rara Ar…®mathiya, va i gogomwau na iye Jiu lenji kot lagh…®ye lenji randeviva regha. Iye va amala thovuye na i ghambu Jisas Krais. Hu thuwe Mat 27:57-60; Mak 15:42-46; Luk 23:50-53; Jon 19:38-42.  
\li1 6. Josep Basabas, Jisas gharaghambu regha. Va ina weya Jisas va irikowe. MbaŇča va th…® tuthiya ghal…®Ňčae gharaghamb…® regha na Judas ghath…®th…®, th…® tuthi weŇčgiya Josep Basabas na Mataiyas. Loi i tuthi na Mataiyas idae th…® vaidi. Hu thuwe Vak 1:23.  
\li1 7. Josep, idae lagh…®ye Banabas. Hu thuwe Vak 4:36.   
\p
\v 57  \k Josuwa\k* \it [English: Joshua]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Vak 7:45; Hib 4:8). Mosese va i mare na e ghereiye, Josuwa i tabona Isirel lenji randeviva. I viva weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ko na th…® ru Kenani e le val…®vaŇčga, iya Loi va i dageraweko weŇčgi. Th…® gaith…® weŇčgi na th…® kivwalaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ko va th…® yakuko gheko. Amba Josuwa i ghatha Kenani na wabwi wabwiyaworo na wabwiwo, na i giya wabwira iya weŇčgiya uu regha na regha ghambanji, ma mbe Livai eŇčge, kaiwae thiye ravowovowoŇčgi. Josuwa iye randeviva lagh…®ye, na i dage vur…®gheghe weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® na th…® ghambu Loi e gharevatomwe. Va iŇča, ‚ÄúGhino na lo bodaboda, ne wo ghambugha Loi.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 58  \k Juda\k* \it [English: Judah]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Mat 1:2-3; Hib 7:14; 8:8; Vat 5:5; 7:5). Juda iye va Jakob le ŇčgamaŇčgama theyaworo na theghewo regha. Iye orumburumbunji uu idae Juda. Orumburumbunji va th…® yaku Judiya e le val…®vaŇčga. Ghemba Jerusalem ina Judiya. Jisas Krais va i mena uu Juda na i vir…® e ghemba regha idae Bet…®lehem Judiya e tine.   
\p
\v 59  \k Kalsidoni\k* \it [English: chalcedony]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Vat 4:3; 21:11, 18-19). Kalsidoni iye var…® thovuye lagh…®ye, na ma lemoyo inanjiwe. Hu thuwe \bd Var…® thovuthovuye na modanji lagh…®ye\bd*.   
\p
\v 60  \k Kamel\k* \it [English: camel]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Mat 3:4; 19:24; 23:24; Mak 1:6; 10:25; Luk 18:25). Kamel iye thetheghan lagh…®ye iye ghar…®ghar…® th…® thawe na tembe dowe kaiwaeva. MbaŇča vavana vulivuliye th…® vakaiwoŇča na th…® vakatha kwamawe ma modae i lagh…®ye. Kamel ŇčgaliŇčgaliyae ina page ###‚Äď### e lughawoghawo.   
\p
\v 61  \k Kaniliyan\k* \it [English: carnelian]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Vat 4:3; 21:20). Kaniliyan iye var…® ghayamoyamo i thovuye lagh…®ye, na ma lemoyo inanjiwe. Hu thuwe \bd Var…® thovuthovuye na modanji lagh…®ye\bd*.   
\p
\v 62  \k Kein\k* \it [English: Cain]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Hib 11:4; 1Jon 3:12; Jiud 11). Kein va Adam na Ive narinji regha na lagh…®yeniye. Va i yamwakabu ghaghae nasiyeniyewe Abel, kaiwae Loi i wovatha Abel le vowo iye sip, ko iyemaeŇčge i botewo Kein le vowo wit. Iya kaiwae Kein i un…®gh…® Abel. Iyake kaiwae, Loi iŇča na Kein ne i robwabwari yambaneke lagh…®ye na ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye th…® botewo.   
\p
\v 63  \k Kenani\k* \it [English: Canaan]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Mat 15:22; Vak 7:11; 13:19). Kenani iye Loi va i dawerawe na ne i giya weŇčgiya Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye na lenji thelau. Noroke thelauko iyako idae Isirel. MbaŇča vavana th…® uno idae Palestain.   
\p
\v 64  \k Kiten…®yathu thanavuniye\k* \it [English: circumcision]\it* ‚ÄĒ Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye ghanjithanavu regha iye kiten…®yathu thanavuniye. Ňägama gh…®moru regha na regha mbaŇča i wo mbaŇčawa na e ghereiye wo i wo kiten…®yathu thanavuniye. Ghar…®ghar…®ko va th…® vakatha iyako kaiwae Loi va i dagewe Eibraham iye na orumburumbuye mbala th…® vakatha Ňčgoreiye (R…®gh 17:9-14). Kiten…®yathu thanavuniye va nono gharumwaru gh…®moru iye va Jiu. MbaŇča vavana th…® uno Jiu ‚Äúghar…®ghar…® thiye th…® wo kiten…®yathu thanavuniye.‚ÄĚ  
\pi1 MbaŇčaniye ghar…®ghar…® va th…® vavagharekai Toto Thovuye weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®, Jiu vavana va th…®Ňča thela thoŇčgo nuwaiya i tabona Kristiyan ko iye ma Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye regha, iviva ne i wo kiten…®yathu thanavuniye. Iyake ghanono iye i tabona Jiu na i varaeŇča ne i ghambu Mosese le Mbaro. ThoŇčgo va i vakatha iyake, ne e ghereiye val…®kaiwae i tabona Kristiyan. Pol mava i varaeŇča renuwaŇčako iyako. Va i utuŇča iyake e letako va i roriko na i variye weŇčgiya ekelesiya ina Galeisiya. Tembe Ňčgoreiyeva i utuŇčake lemoyo rororiko e t…®ne. Va iŇča mbe bigi regha eŇčge lolo regha wo i vakatha na i tabona Kristiyan, iyake wo i loŇčweghath…® Jisas Krais.   
\p
\v 65  \k Krais\k* \it [English: Christ]\it* ‚ÄĒ Dageke Krais i mena Grik e ghal…®Ňčanji na gharumwaru ‚Äúlolo iye regha th…® varuvu e bunama.‚ÄĚ Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niyeŇčgi dageke Mesaiya tembe gharumwaruva ‚Äúlolo regha va th…® varuvu e bunama.‚ÄĚ MbaŇča va i vivako mbaŇča Loi i tuthiya Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye lenji kiŇč, ravowovowo lagh…®ye va i varuvu e bunama na iyake i tabona nono i govwambwara amalagh…®niye va i tuthi na kiŇč. Ko mbaŇča Loi i dagerawe iŇča ne i variye Ravamoru na i vamoruŇčgiya le ghar…®ghar…® na i womena vwenyevwenye Loi le mbaro, i uno idae ‚ÄúMesaiya‚ÄĚ o ‚ÄúKrais,‚ÄĚ na i vatomwe iye ghamberegha va i tuthi na i variye.   
\p
\v 66  \k Krisolait\k* \it [English: chrisolite]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Vat 4:3; 21:11, 18-19). Krisolait iye var…® thovuye lagh…®ye, na ma lemoyo inanjiwe. Hu thuwe \bd Var…® thovuthovuye na modanji lagh…®ye\bd*.   
\p
\v 67  \k Kros\k* \it [English: cross]\it* ‚ÄĒ Kros iye Rom lenji rambarombaro ghanjithanavu th…® lith…® rakaiv…® e mare e kros vwatae. Iyake lith…® weŇčgi ragabo, ghar…®ghar…® thavala th…® kaiv…® bwagabwaga. Ra vakatha kros ra wo tu weiye umbwa regha nasiye i valawe i mborowae. Rakaiv…® va th…® vur…®gheghe ŇčgeŇčge na th…® wo kros na th…® wa iya ghembako ne veth…® gaboŇčgikowe. Iyako ragagaith…® th…® tagavatad…® lolokowe e krosko o th…® li thiyo na th…® Ňčgar…®ghath…®we. Amba th…® vwandan krosiko na th…® teteya loloko i kwate gheko ghaghad i mare. Lolo th…® rokros Ňčgoraiyake wo i ghataŇča v…®r…® lagh…®ye amba muyai i mare. Gharegaith…® kaiwae na th…® tagavamare e kros. Jisas iŇča thoŇčgo lolo regha nuwaiya na gharaghambu wo i renuwaŇča valaweya ghamberegha na i wo gha kros na i ghambugha Jisas (Mat 10:38; 16:24; Mak 8:34; Luk 9:23; 14:27). Iyake gharumwaru Jisas gharaghambu mbe th…® roroghagha na th…® ghataŇča v…®r…® iya kaiwae na th…® vatomweŇčgi na th…® mare kaiwae.   
\p
\v 68  \k Lepelo\k* \it [English: leprosy]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Mat 8:3; Mak 1:42; Luk 5:12-13; 7:22; na vavana). Lepelo iye ghambwera regha. Buk Boboma e t…®ne utuke ‚Äúlepeloke‚ÄĚ iye njimwa ghaghambwera iya ma mboromboro weiye ‚Äúleprosy‚ÄĚ noroke. Thiye va th…® ghambweraŇča lepelo ma val…®kaiwanji na th…® yaku weinjiyaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® ma th…® ghambweraŇča. Ghar…®ghar…®ko thovuthovuye ma th…® yaku weiyaŇčgiya thavala th…® ghataŇča lepelo. Ma th…® utu weŇčgi. Ma val…®kaiwae th…® kururu weya Loi e Ňčgolo kururu o Ňägolo Boboma e t…®nenji.   
\p
\v 69  \k Livai\k* \it [English: Levi]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Hib 7:5, 9-10; Vat 7:7). Livai iye va theyaworo na theghewoma regha Jeikob le ŇčgamaŇčgamaŇčgi. Livai orumburumbuyeŇčgi va th…® ghatharaŇčgiyaŇčgi na th…® kaiwo Loi le Ngolo Boboma e t…®ne. Ravowovowo thiye va th…® tuthiŇčgi th…® mena Livai orumbrumbuye weŇčgi. I mboromboro weya Eron ghauu. Hu thuwe \bd Eron\bd*.  
\pi1 Livai tembe lolo reghava idae. Iye va Jisas ghal…®Ňčae gharaghambu theyaworo na theghewoma regha. MbaŇča vavana th…® uno idae Matiu (Mat 9:9; Mak 2:14; Luk 5:27-29). Iye va Toto Thovuye Matiu gharorori.   
\p
\v 70  \k Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu\k* \it [English: prophet]\it* ‚ÄĒ Ghal…®Ňčae gharautu iye lolo i uturaŇčgiya totoko Loi i woraŇčgiyakowe weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® Loi kaiwae.  
\pi1 Buk Boboma Teuye ghambaŇča Loi va i variyeŇčgi ghal…®Ňčae gharautuko lemoyo, Ňčgoreiye Samuwel, Aiseya na Jeremaiya. Lemi utuutu e t…®nenji Loi i woraŇčgiya bigibigiko lemoyo ne th…® yomara. Ghal…®Ňčae gharautuko mbaŇča vavana th…® rorinjoŇča totoko thiyako, na thiyake ra vaidi Buk Boboma Teuye ghabuk idaidanji Ňčgoreiye Aiseya na Jeremaiya. Va i vivako amba muyai Jisas i vir…®, th…® utuŇča le mena na budakai ne i yomarawe. Tembe th…® utuŇčava bigibigi lemoyo ne th…® yomara mbaŇča yambaneke e le ghambako, amba muyai Jisas Krais ne i njoghama na i ghatha yambaneke.  
\pi1 Buk Boboma Togha e t…®nenji, mbaŇča vavana th…® utuŇča ‚ÄúLoi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu.‚ÄĚ Hu thuwe Jon 1:21. GhaliŇčae gharutuke iyake iye th…® utuŇčake Mba 18:15-18. Iye ghal…®Ňčae gharautu i lagh…®ye iya Loi va i dagerawe ne i variye.  
\pi1 Buk Boboma Togha e t…®ne, ghar…®ghar…® th…® utuutu Nyao Boboma le vur…®gheghe e t…®ne, thiye th…® uno idanji ghal…®Ňčae gharautu, kaiwae va th…® utuŇča totoko Loi i woraŇčgiyako weŇčgi.   
\p
\v 71  \k Loi le ghamba mbaro\k* \it [English: Kingdom of God]\it* ‚ÄĒ Utuke thiya th…® utuŇča Loi Ňčgoreiye rambarombaro o kiŇč, na ghar…®ghar…® ngoreiye le ghamba mbaro ghar…®ghar…®niye. KiŇč i mbaroŇčaŇčgiya le ghar…®ghar…®, na Loi Ňčgoreiye kiŇč kaiwae i ndeganagana le ghar…®ghar…® na i giya weŇčgi bigibigiko wolagh…®ye nuwanjiya na i viva weŇčgi na i mbaroŇčaŇčgi. Loi le ghamba mbaro ghar…®ghar…®niye thiye th…® var…®minje na th…® ghambu Loi. Va Jisas i mena e yambaneke, Loi le ghamba mbaro i yomara e kamwath…® togha kaiwae Jisas Krais i vugha kamwath…® togha na ghar…®ghar…® th…® ru Loi le ghamba mbaro.  
\pi1 Loi le ghamba mbaro ina aŇčganiye ghar…®ghar…® th…® varaeŇča Loi iye lenji kiŇč. MbaŇča Jisas ne i njoghama, Loi le ghamba mbaro ne i mboromboro, na ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye ne th…® thuwe wagiyawe.   
\p
\v 72  \k Loi le Sip Nariye\k* \it [English: Lamb of God]\it* ‚ÄĒ Jon Rabap…®taiso va i uno Jisas Loi le Sip Nariye Jon 1:29, 36 e t…®nenji. Jiu va ghanjithanavu, mbe th…® vovo sip nariye weya Loi mbala Loi ne i numoten lenji thar…®. MbaŇča sip nariye i mare kaiwae madibae i voruraŇčgi na i voruyathu, iyake Ňčgoreiye lolo iye i vakatha thar…® na i mare. Sip nariye iye thar…® gharavakatha ghath…®th…®. Na loloko iyako i th…®nava Loi e marae. Jisas th…® uno Loi le Sip Nariye kaiwae va i giya yawaliye Ňčgoreiye vowo mbala la thar…® Loi ne i numoten…®Ňčgi. Vatomwe VaŇčgothiye 5 Sip Nariye i meth…® Krais.   
\p
\v 73  \k Loi Nariye\k* \it [English: Son of God]\it* ‚ÄĒ Iye Jisas Krais idae regha. MbaŇča ra vaona Buk Boboma ra thuwe Loi iye mbe regha eŇčge. Loi iye ma e r…®gher…®ghe na va i vakatha bigibigike wolagh…®ye. Tembe ra thuweva Buk Boboma e t…®ne Loi i tabona lolo mbaŇča Jisas Krais i vir…® (Jon 1:1, 14-15). Jisas i utu weya Loi na iŇča ramae. Loi i utu e buruburu na iŇča Jisas iye nariye. Ko iyemaeŇčge idake iyake ‚ÄúLoi Nariye‚ÄĚ ma gharumwaru Jisas ne e yawayawaliye Ňčgoreiye lolo regha na regha nariye. MbaŇča ra vavaona Buk Boboma ra thuwe Ramae na Nariye thiye mboromboroŇčgi. Thenjighewoko thiye Loi. Thenjighewoko ma e r…®gher…®ghe na ma e lenji ghambako. Thiye mboromboro e bigibigi wolagh…®ye. Mbwata idake iyake, Loi Nariye, i vatomwe Jisas i ghambu ramae le renuwaŇča mbaŇča i mena e yambaneke na i vamoruŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®. Ra thuwe Ramae na Nariye thiye Loi regha na ra loŇčweghath…®, othembe ma ra ghareghare ŇčgoroŇčga val…®kaiwanji. Ra ghareghareŇča ghar…®ghar…®, na Loi iye mbe tomethi. Bigibigike wolagh…®ye ra ghareghare Loi kaiwae, mbe ra ghareghare eŇčge kaiwae i woraŇčgi weinda.   
\p
\v 74  \k LoŇčweghath…® weya Jisas Krais\k* \it [English: believing in Jesus Christ]\it* ‚ÄĒ LoŇčweghath…® ma Ňčgoreiye hu loŇčweghath…® Jisas mava i yaku e yambaneke. Ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye th…® loŇčweghath…® iyako. LoŇčweghath…® weya Jisas Krais Ňčgoraiyake: Hu loŇčweghath…® budakaiya Jisas va iŇča ghamberegha i emunjoru. Hu wovatha le vavaghare wolagh…®ye. Tembe gharumwaruva iyake: U tuthi Jisas iye Ravamoru na Giya, na u ghambu na u tabona ghal…®Ňčae gharaghambu.   
\p
\v 75  \k Lolo Nariye\k* \it [English: Son of Man]\it* ‚ÄĒ Va i vivako amba muyai Jisas Krais i vir…®, Loi i vatomwe weya ghal…®Ňčae gharautu Daniyel budakai ne i yomara mbaŇča i menamenake t…®ne. Daniyel i thuweya lolo regha i njama e ngal…®ngal…®l…®ko buruburu e t…®ne. Loloko i njama weiye le vur…®gheghe lagh…®ye moli na vwenyevwenye. I mena Loi e marae na amalagh…®niye i giya mbaro na i mbaronaŇčgiya vanautumake wolagh…®ye na ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye mbaŇča ma e le ghambako. Daniyel ma i ghareghare loloke iyake me thuwe iye thela. Va i rori othembe i mena e buruburu, ghayamoyamo Ňčgoreiye ‚Äúlolo nariye.‚ÄĚ Gharumwaru, ghayamoyamo ngoreiye lolo. Buk Boboma Togha e t…®ne, mbaŇčaviye Jisas i uno ghamberegha ‚ÄúLolo Nariye.‚ÄĚ MbaŇča va i vakatha iyake, i woraŇčgiya iye ghamberegha iya Daniyel va iŇča ne i mena.   
\p
\v 76  \k Lot\k* \it [English: Lot]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Luk 17:28-32; 2Pit 2:7). Lot iye Haran nariye, Eibraham ghaghae nasiyeniye. Lot iŇča Eibraham iye ramae. (Hu thuwe \bd Eibraham\bd*.) MbaŇča Eibraham va i wa na ve tamweya vanautuma togha Loi va i dagerawe ne i wogiyawe. Amba muyai veth…® ru vanautumako iyako. Lot va i wa ve yaku e ghemba lagh…®ye Sodoma. Ghar…®ghar…® Sodoma va th…® vakavakatha vakatha raraithar…® lemoyo. Ko iyake kaiwae Loi iŇča ne i mukuwo ghembako iyako. Loi i variye le nyao thovuye ve dage vur…®gheghe weya Lot na i vo amba i variye nd…®ghe. Amba Lot na le ŇčgaŇčga th…® wareri. Ko amba Loi i mukuwo ghembako iyako e nd…®ghe. Nyao thovuye va i dage weŇčgi Lot thava ne th…® maranjogha e ghereinji mbaŇča th…® iteteya ghembako lagh…®ye, ko Lot levo i gh…®maranjogha na e mbaŇčako vara iyako i tabonavara njigh…® i mbumbu na Ňčgoreiye var…® lagh…®ye.   
\p
\v 77  \k Manna\k* \it [English: manna]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Jon 6:31, 49, 58; Hib 9:4; Vat 2:17). Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® voraŇčgi Ijipt e t…®ne na e ghereiye, thiye th…® loŇčgatako theghathegha ghwevar…® e vur…®vur…® vwatavwata. MbaŇčaŇčgiko thiyako e t…®nenji Loi i vakatha ghamba rotaele na i giya ghan…®Ňčga na th…® ghan. Ghan…®Ňčgake iyake idae ‚Äúmanna.‚ÄĚ Va i mena e buruburu na i dobunja yambaneke mbaŇča regha na regha, mbe mbaŇča Sabat eŇčge. Ghar…®ghar…®ko va th…® mwanavathavatha. Hu thuwe RaŇč 16:13-36.   
\p
\v 78  \k Mas…®ted\k* \it [English: mustard]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Mat 13:31-32; 17:20; Mak 4:31-32; Luk 13:19; 17:6). Mas…®tedke iyake iye umbwa regha ghar…®ghar…® th…® kabu e lenji uma na th…® vakaiwoŇča kaiwae i vakatha ghaŇčiŇčga gham…®nae thovuye, Ňčgoreiye th…® vakaiwoŇča njigh…®. Mbombouye mbe nanasiye moli, ko iyemaeŇčge i mbuthu na umbwa lagh…®ye moli. (Iyake ma ndiya th…® ghawi weiye gh…®leth…®.)   
\p
\v 79  \k Matabwaya\k* \it [English: crown]\it* ‚ÄĒ Matabwaya ghathuwathuwa theghewo. Mwatabwaya kiŇčko i th…®n…®ko i govambwara iye le ghamba mbaroko. Matabwaya regha va th…® wogiya iye yavwatata gha nono weya lolo i wo rukurukuko modae o mwadiwo reghava, o ragagaith…® iye ma i maramaru iye i kivwalaŇčgiya ghath…®gh…®yaŇčgi e gaith…®.   
\p
\v 80  \k Mbaro\k* \it [English: law]\it* ‚ÄĒ Loi le Mbaro va th…® rorinjoŇča Buk Boboma Teuye bukuniyeŇčgi mbambalima iviva e t…®nenji. Mbaro vara Loi va i wogiyawe Mosese ghar…®ghar…® ghanjithovuye kaiwae inanji gheko, na tembe Ňčgorieyeva ghar…®ghar…® na Isirel va th…® rikowe utuutuniye. Hu thuwe \bd Mosese\bd*.   
\p
\v 81  \k Mbaro gharavavaghare\k* \it [English: scribes, teachers of the law]\it* ‚ÄĒ Thiye va th…® vavaghareŇča Loi le mbaro. Th…® vavaghareŇča bigibigi va th…® rorinjoŇča Mosese le buk mbambalima. Hu thuwe \bd Mbaro \bd*na \bd Mosese\bd*.   
\p
\v 82  \k Mbemba\k* \it [English: fasting]\it* ‚ÄĒ Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye ghanjithanavu regha iye th…®mbe ghan…®Ňčga. Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye e t…®nenji iyake th…® uturaŇčgiya lenji thar…® na th…® roiteteŇčgi ghanono. O iyake nuwathar…® ghanono o th…® menawe Loi na th…® wonjoŇča ghanjimberegha e le mbaro raberabe.   
\p
\v 83  \k Mbwana Ňägoreiye\k* \it [English: amen]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Rom 1:25, 9:5; 1Kor 14:16; 2Kor 1:20; na vavana). Jiu e ghal…®Ňčangiko, utuke th…®Ňčake Mbwana Ňägoreiye gharumwaru ‚Äúmbe Ňčgoreiyevara,‚ÄĚ ‚Äúiyake i emunjoru.‚ÄĚ MbaŇča lolo regha i naŇčgo, ghar…®ghar…®ko vavana th…® varaeŇča, th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúMbwana Ngoreiye.‚ÄĚ Vat 3:14, Jisas iye th…® uno th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúMbwana Ňägoreiye‚ÄĚ, kaiwae iye emunjoru.   
\p
\v 84  \k Mwata lagh…®ye moli\k* \it [English: dragon]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Vat 12:3; 13:4; 16:13; 20:2). Mwata lagh…®ye moli iye riuriu thetheghaniye le vur…®gheghe i lagh…®ye moli. Ghathuwathuwa Ňčgoreiye yeŇčg…®yeŇčg…® lagh…®ye regha ko iyemaeŇčge tembe th…® unova idae mwata. Vatomwe e t…®ne mwatake iyake th…® vakaiwoŇča na i meth…® Seitan iye nyaoko wolagh…®ye ghanjigiya lagh…®ye. Buk Boboma Teuye vavana th…® utuŇča mwatake iyake utuutuniye, meth…® utuniye i menawe. Mwata lagh…®ye ma mbaŇča regha th…® yaku e yambaneke.   
\p
\v 85  \k Melkisedek\k* \it [English: Melchizedek]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Hib 5:6-10; 6:20; 7:1-17). Melkisedek ghaghareghare mbe seiwo eŇčge ra ghareghare na i mena Buk Boboma e t…®ne, Hibru na R…®gh 14:17-20. Rororike thiyake iŇča Melkisedek iye va Loi le tututhi ravowovowoniye regha. Va mbaŇčaniye, th…®gh…®yaŇčgi th…® yalawe Eibrahan nariye Lot na le boda na lenji bigibigiko wolagh…®ye. Eibraham na le ragagaith…® th…® wa veth…® gaith…® weŇčgi na th…® kivwalaŇčgi. I vamoruŇčgiya Lot na lenji bigibigiko wolagh…®ye. MbaŇča Eibraham va i njogha na e kamwath…® mborowae, Melkisedek i lavolevole. Melkisedek i giya bred na waen weya Eibraham na i naŇčgo weya Loi mbe gharewe. Eibraham va i vakatha bigibigiko i biginjoghako wabwiyaworo na i giya wabwira Melkisedekwe. Theghathegha ighanagha muyai i tabona Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye ghanjithanavu regha na th…® giya wabwira i mena lenji uloulo na lenji kaiwo modanji.  
\pi1 Isirel lenji ravowovowoko wolagh…®ye th…® tuthiya Livai e ghauu t…®ne. Ko iyemaeŇčge Melkisedek ghambaŇča e t…®ne, Livai ma i vir…®. Eibraham nariye Aisake, ne Livai rumbuye, ma tembe iye i vir…®va. Iya kaiwae mbaŇča Eibraham va i giya wabwira Melkisedekwe, va ngoreiye ravowovowoko wolagh…®ye Livai ghauu e t…®ne th…® giyawe, kaiwae mbaŇča muyai, mbaŇča ne th…® vir…®, thiye ne Eibraham orumburumbuye (Hib 7:9-10).   
\p
\v 86  \k Mer\k* \it [English: myrrh]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Mat 2:11; Mak 15:23; Jon 19:39; Vat 18:13). Mer iye bigi regha modae i lagh…®ye. Butiye i thovuye. Th…® vakatha e umbwa regha thiye. Jiu va th…® vakaiwoŇča Ňčgoreiye merisin kaiwae i vakatha lolo i ghena seiwo ma i gham…®no v…®r…® lagh…®ye. Tembe th…® vakaiwoŇčava beku kaiwae.   
\p
\v 87  \k Meri\k* \it [English: Mary]\it* ‚ÄĒ Meri lemoyo tomethi inanji Buk Boboma Togha e t…®ne.  
\li1 1. Meri Jisas t…®nae.  
\li1 2. Meri t…®nan Magadala. Jisas va i vakatha na nyao raraithar…® theghepir…® th…® raŇčgiwe, na i tabona gharaghambu eunda (Mat 27:55-56; Mak 16:9; Luk 8:2; Jon 20:1-2; 11-18, na r…®ghethoru vavana).  
\li1 3. Meri t…®nan Betani, Mata ghaghae moli na Lasarus iye lounji. Va i yaku Jisas e gheghe na i vandeŇče le vavaghare (Luk 10:38-42; Jon 11:1-5; 12:1-7).  
\li1 4. Meri Jemes na Josep t…®nanji. Merike iyake mbwata mboromboro weiye Meri Kilopas levo (Mat 27:56; Mak 15:40; 16:1; Luk 24:10).  
\li1 5. Meri Jon Mak t…®nae. Merike iyake e le Ňčgolo ina Jerusalem, iya Jisas gharaghambu va th…® mevathavathawe (Vak 12:12).   
\p
\v 88  \k Mesaiya\k* \it [English: Messiah]\it* ‚ÄĒ Hu thuwe \bd Krais\bd*.   
\p
\v 89  \k Mevathavatha Ňägoloniye\k* \it [English: tabernacle, tent of meeting]\it* ‚ÄĒ Va i vivako, mbaŇča Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye mbe th…® loŇčgaloŇčga vuruvuru vwatavwata e t…®ne, Loi i dage weya Mosese na i vakatha Ňčgolo tomethi. Loi va i dage na i vakatha weiye kwama thovuye moli na thetheghan njimwae. Val…®kaiwae le rakanjoŇča i maya na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva le vatavatad i maya. Ghar…®ghar…® th…® bigi mbaŇča th…® loŇčgaloŇčga. Amba th…® vatavatad…®va.  
\pi1 Dagerawe gha Bogis th…® th…®n…®rawe e t…®ne, Woluwolu Boboma Moli e t…®ne. Var…®var…® Loi va i rorinjoŇča le Mbaro theyaworo ina e t…®ne, weiyaŇčgiya bigibigi vavana. Hu thuwe \bd Dagerawe gha Bogis\bd*.  
\pi1 Va i vivako Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye va th…® kururu weya Loi Mevathavatha Ňägoloniye e t…®ne, na th…® vowowe. Th…® vakatha ghaghad Solomon va i vatad…® Ňägolo Boboma Jerusalem e t…®ne. Hu thuwe Mevathavatha Ňägoloniye ŇčgaliŇčgaliyae page ###.  
\pi1 \k Mosese\k* \it [English: Moses]\it* ‚ÄĒ Mosese va Isirel lenji randeviva lagh…®ye moli. MbaŇčaniye Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye va rakakaiwobwaga Ijipt e t…®ne, Loi i tuthi Moses na i viva weŇčgi na th…® raŇčgiwe na th…® njogha thelauko kaero va i giyako weŇčgi. Loi va i lavolevole Mosese e numowo kamwath…®niye. Ee, Mosese va i thuwe nd…®ghema i ra e umbwaumbwa ndamwandamwa, ko iyemaeŇčge mava i nda. Mosese i ghareghare Loi va ina gheko. Amba Loi i dagewe na iŇča ne i vaŇčgunjogha le ghar…®ghar…® e lenji vanautumako.  
\pi1 Loi va i vakaiwoŇča Mosese na i vakatha vakatha ghamba rotaele. MbaŇča regha Ijipt lenji ragagaith…® th…® vagevagegeŇčgiya Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye, th…® mena Njigh…® Sosoro. Loi va i vakatha ndewendewe i rowo lagh…®ye na i unjogha mbwa, mbala mbwa i ndeghath…® Ňčgoreiye baba vaŇčga na vaŇčga na e lughawoghawo thelau i mwa. Ghar…®ghar…®ko th…® loŇčga ghathara e lughawoghawoko. MbaŇča ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye th…® vuthavao e val…®vaŇčga, Ijipt lenji ragagaith…® th…® vutha na th…® mando na tembene th…® vakathava Ňčgoreiye. Ko iyemaeŇčge mbwako va i njogha e ghambae na i vagumoŇčgi na th…® munumare.  
\pi1 Mosese iye Loi va i giya le mbarowe Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye kaiwanji. MbaŇča va th…® lawa Njigh…® Sosoro na e ghereiye, th…® loŇčgao ghaghad…® th…® mena ouko idae Sainai. Mosese ghamberegha i voro Sainai na i yaku gheko na i naŇčgo weya Loi. Loi va i dage weya Mosese na i utugiya le mbarowe. Loi va i rorinjoŇča mbaroko theyaworo lagh…®ye moli e var…® var…®iwo; mbaŇča ubotu e ghereiye Mosese i du na i diviyaviya var…®ko thiyako kaiwae i gharegaith…® lagh…®ye mbaŇča i thuweya ghar…®ghar…®ko th…® kururu weya loi kwankwan. MbaŇča amba Loi i dagewe na i vakatha var…® totogha, na Loi va i rorinjoŇčava mbaroko theyaworoko. Theghathegha lemoyo var…®iwoko inanji Dagerawe gha Bogis iya ina Mevathavatha Ňägoloniye e t…®ne.  
\pi1 MbaŇčaniye va i njama Ou Sainai e ghereiye, Mosese i rorinjoŇča mbaroko wolagh…®ye. Mbaroko thiyako inanji Buk Boboma Teuye ghanjibuk iviva mbambalima e t…®nenji. Ghar…®ghar…® tembe th…® unova idanji ‚ÄúMosese le buk…®Ňčgi.‚ÄĚ Idaidanji R…®ghenda, RaŇčgi, Livai, Lenji Ghanaghanagha, na Mbaro. Hu thuwe \bd Mbaro\bd*.   
\p
\v 90  \k Naaman\k* \it [English: Naaman]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Luk 4:27). Naaman va i yaku vanautuma regha idae Siriya. Iye ragagaith…® lenji randeviva na iye ma Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niyeko regha. Othembe iye ida lagh…®ye, i ghataŇča lepelo. MbaŇča va i loŇčwe Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu Ilaisa utuniye, i mena na i nango i vamoru kaiwae lepelo e t…®ne. Ilaisa va i dagewe na i wa Walagh…®ta Jor…®dan na ve thithu ghamberegha mbaŇčapir…®. Naaman va i ghambu ghal…®Ňčae na lepelo iko moli.   
\p
\v 91  \k Nad\k* \it [English: nard]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Mak 14:3; Jon 12:3). MbaŇča regha ela eunda i th…®n…®mena bunama regha idae nad na i varuvo Jisas gheghewe. Th…® vakatha nad e umbwa regha thiye idae spaikenad.   
\p
\v 92  \k Ňägile\k* \it [English: pearl]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Mat 7:6; 13:45-46; 1Tim 2:9; Vat 17:4; 18:12, 16; 21:21). Ňägile iye bigi regha modae lagh…®ye moli. Iye ghayamoyamo i thovuye. I ndalandala na i kaleva. Ghar…®ghar…® th…® vakaiwoŇča na th…® vakatha numonji ghae na tembe th…® vakathava ghavatha ghar…®ghar…® kaiwanji.   
\p
\v 93  \k Ňägolo Boboma\k* \it [English: Temple]\it* ‚ÄĒ Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye lenji Ňägolo Boboma ina Jerusalem, va ghemba lagh…®ye moli ina Isirel. Solomon va i vatad…® Ňägolo Boboma iviva na bigibigi boboma va inanji Mevathavatha Ňägoloniye, th…® bigiraweŇčgiwe. MbaŇčako iyako na i ghaoko, Ňägolo Boboma mbe iye eŇčge vara ghar…®ghar…® val…®kaiwae th…® vowo weya Loi. Iya kaiwae Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye mbe th…® wawawe Jerusalem thaga lagh…®ye kaiwanji na mbowo th…® wava th…® vowo weya Loi. Hu thuwe \bd Solomon\bd*.  
\pi1 Muyai Isirel ghath…®gh…®yaŇčgi th…® kivwala Jerusalem. Th…® mukuwo Ňägoloko Boboma na th…® mban…®raŇčgiya Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye lemoyo th…® wa Babilon. MbaŇča th…® vatomweŇčgiya Jiu na th…® njogha Jerusalem, th…® vatad…®va Ňägolo Boboma. Theghathegha lemoyo e ghereiye KiŇč Herod iye i lagh…®ye i vatad Ňägolo Boboma togha na Ňägolo Boboma teuye ghath…®th…®. Ňägoloko Boboma iyako va ina Jerusalem mbaŇča Jisas i vir…®.  
\pi1 Ňägolo Boboma ŇčgaliŇčgaliyae ina page ###. Ghayayao va lagh…®ye moli na ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye val…®kaiwae th…® ruwe, mambe Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye eŇčge. Va gheko Jisas i vagevagege raŇčgiyaŇčgiya thetheghan gharakunekune. E t…®ne va ghayayao regha mbe Jiu gh…®mogh…®moru eŇčge th…® ruwe. E t…®ne moli va ghayayao regha. Gheko mbe ravowovowo eŇčge th…® ruwe. E t…®neko va ghamba vowo na gaeba lagh…®ye moli thavwi kaiwae. E ghayayaoko t…®ne moli iyako e t…®ne va Ňägolo Boboma vara weiye woluwolu theghewo, Woluwolu Boboma na Woluwolu Boboma Moli. Bigibigi vavana boboma va th…® vakaiwoŇča th…® kururuwe Loi va inanji Woluwolu Boboma e t…®ne. Dagerawe gha Bogis va ina Woluwolu Boboma Moli, na Loi manjamanjalawae i mbilewe. Mbe Ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye lenji randeviva eŇčge val…®kaiwae i ruwe, na i ruwe mbe mbaŇča regha eŇčge theghathegha regha na regha. Kwama i molao i ganatena Woluwolu Boboma Moli. MbaŇča Jisas i mare, kwamako i mathethewa yavoro na ve wo bode (Mat 27:51; Mak 15:38; Luk 23.45). Iyake i vatomwe Loi va i vugha kamwath…® ghar…®ghar…® val…®kaiwae th…® ru e marae, thoŇčgo th…® loŇčweghath…® Jisas Krais.   
\p
\v 94  \k Ňägolo Kururu\k* \it [English: synagogue, house of worship]\it* ‚ÄĒ Ňägolo kururu iye Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye lenji ghamba mevathavatha, mbe Sabat e t…®ne vara. Ňägolo kururu regha ina ghemba regha na regha Isirel e t…®ne. Ňägoloko kururu e t…®nenji va th…® vaona Buk Boboma na th…® vavaghareŇča Loi le mbaro. Ghar…®ghar…®ko va th…® naŇčgo weya Loi gheko na th…® kururuwe. MbaŇča vavana th…® vakatha kot e t…®nenji. Va i vivako, utuke iyake gharumwaru ma iŇča Ňčgolo kaiwae, ko iyemaeŇčge iŇča ghar…®ghar…® th…® mevathavatha gheko kaiwanji.   
\p
\v 95  \k Ninive\k* \it [English: Nineveh]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Mat 12:41; Luk 11:30, 32). Ninive va ghemba regha idae, iya Loi va i variye Jona na ve vavaghareŇča toto weŇčgi. Loi le toto va iye ne i mukuwo Ninive kaiwae th…® vakavakatha vakatha raraithar…®. MbaŇča th…® loŇčwe Jona le vavaghare weŇčgi, th…® randa na th…® uturaŇčgiya lenji thar…® na th…® roiteteŇčgi. Iyake kaiwae Loi i numoten…®Ňčgi na ma i mukuwoŇčgi. Hu thuwe \bd Jona\bd*.   
\p
\v 96  \k Njigh…® Sosoro\k* \it [English: Red Sea]\it* ‚ÄĒ Njigh…®ke iyake ina Isirel na Ijipt e ghanjilughawoghawo. Hu thuwe Rom Ghaghambambaro ghamap. Hu thuwe \bd Mosese\bd*.   
\p
\v 97  \k Nowa\k* \it [English: Noah]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Mat 24:37-38; Luk 3:36; 17:26-27; Hib 11:7; 1Pit 3:20; 2Pit 2:5). Nowa va i yaku e yambaneke va i vivako. Nowa utuniye ina Buk Boboma Teuye buk iviva idae R…®ghenda, Vangothiye 6 ghaghad…® 9. Nowa ghambaŇča ghar…®ghar…®ko va th…® vakatha vakatha raraithar…® lemoyo. Iyake kaiwae, Loi iŇča ne i variye ŇčgonuŇčgo na i mukuwo ghar…®ghar…®ko na bigibigiko wolagh…®ye inanji e yambaneke. Ko iyemaeŇčge Nowa va lolo thovuye; i ghambugha Loi. Iya kaiwae Loi i dagewe Nowa na i vatad…® waŇčga lagh…®ye moli, na i dage ŇčgoroŇčga ne i vakatha na iŇča. I dagewe Nowa ne weiyaŇčgiya levo na le ŇčgaŇčga thegheto na lenji ovo th…® tha e waŇčgako. Tembe Ňčgoreiyeva ne i vaŇčgudowe gh…®moru na wevo thetheghanke wolagh…®ye tomethi na make wolagh…®ye tomethi. Ne i vaŇčgudowe thetheghan gh…®moru na wevo thenjighepir…® iya. Nowa va i vakatha wagiyawe Ňčgoreiye Loi va i dagewe. Th…® tha e waŇčga na e ghereiye, Loi i variye uye, uyevwelagh…® lagh…®ye moli, na ŇčgonuŇčgo. Mbwako i thotho na i kivwalaŇčgiya ouou vwatavwatanji. Ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye e yambeneke thiya munja na th…® mare, mbe Nowa na le bodaboda eŇčge Loi i vamoruŇčgi.  
\pi1 Theghathegha regha e ghereiye na iko, mbwako i dinja na thelauko i mwa. Nowa na le bodaboda th…® raŇčgi e waŇčgako. Amba Nowa i vakatha vowo weya Loi na i taraweŇča kaiwae va i vamoruŇčgi. Loi va i dagerawe ma mbaŇča reghava ne i vakatha ŇčgonuŇčgo Ňčgoreiye iyako. Amba bwawo i yomara e buruburuko. Loi va iŇča bwawo iye le dagerawe ghanono na ma mbaŇča reghava ne i mukuwo yambaneke lagh…®ye.   
\p
\v 98  \k Nyao thovuye\k* \it [English: angel]\it* ‚ÄĒ Nyao thovuthovuye Loi le toto gharawo thiye. Th…® yaku e ghamwae. Totoke gharawo thiyake, nyaoŇčgi, ma ghar…®ghar…®Ňčgi. Mane ghar…®ghar…® th…® thuweŇčgi, ghaghad…®Ňčgi ne th…® govwambwara ghanjimberegha.  
\pi1 Loi i variyeŇčgi le nyao thovuthovuye ne th…® kaiwo kaiwae. Thiye ghanji kaiwo th…® njimbukikiŇčgiya Loi le ghar…®ghar…® (Vak 12:6-11; 27:23; Hib 1:14). MbaŇča vavana Loi i variyeŇčgi na veth…® utu utu i tomethi weya lolo regha.  
\pi1 Nyao thovuthovuye ghanji giya lagh…®ye idae Maikal (Jiud 9). Nyao thovuye lagh…®ye regha idae Geibriyel (Luk 1:19,26).   
\p
\v 99  \k Nyao Boboma\k* \it [English: Holy Spirit]\it* ‚ÄĒ MbaŇča ra vaona Buk Boboma ra vaidi Nyao Boboma iye Loi na othembe iye mberegha. La Loi Jisas Krais Ramae, na i mena weya Jisas Krais, Loi Nariye. Thiye th…® variye Nyao Boboma na i yaku weiyaŇčgiya thavala th…® loŇčweghath…® Jisas Krais na le kaiwo i woraŇčgiya emunjoru weŇčgi, i viva weŇčgi, na i vakathaŇčgi val…®kaiwanji th…® vakatha budakaiya Loi i warariŇča. Kaiwae iye nyao, ma val…®kaiwae ghar…®ghar…® th…® thuwe, othembe ina raloŇčweloŇčweghath…®ke wolagh…®ye weŇčgi. Iya kaiwae Loi iye thegheto, ma theghewo, na thiye theghetoke mboromborongi. Ramae iye Loi, Nariye iye Loi, na Nyao Boboma iye Loi. Ko iyemaeŇčge thiye ma Loi thegheto th…® tomethi, thiye mbe Loi reghaŇčgi vara. Kaiwae Buk Boboma i woraŇčgiya wagiyawe mbe Loi regha eŇčge iye Loi emunjoru. Hu thuwe \bd Loi Nariye\bd*.   
\p
\v 100  \k Nyao raithar…®\k* \it [English: evil spirit]\it* ‚ÄĒ Nyao raraithar…® thiye Seitan le rakakaiwoŇčgi. MbaŇča vavana th…® vakowana ghar…®ghar…® na th…® vakatha na ma th…® ghambugha Loi. IyemaeŇčge th…® ghambu Seitan. MbaŇča vavana th…® ru lolo regha e t…®ne na th…® vambaroŇča. Iyake mbe i emunjoruvara thoŇčgo loloko i vakatha Seitan le kaiwo na ghathanavu na bigibigi raraithar…®.   
\p
\v 101  \k Oliv…®\k* \it [English: olive]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Rom 11:17, 24; Jem 3:12; Vat 11:4). Oliv…® iye umbwa regha i rau na une thovuye. Oliv…® ŇčgaliŇčgaliyae ina page ###‚Äď### e lughawoghawo. Oliv…® uneune th…® uno oliv…®, Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® vakaiwoŇčangi na th…® vakatha bunama gaga kaiwae, na bunama umbaliye ndamwandamwa kaiwae, na bigibigi lemoyo kaiwanji. Oliv…® iye bigi lagh…®ye moli Jiu lenji yakuyaku kaiwae. Ou regha ina Jerusalem ghadidiye, na idae Oliv…® ghanji Ou kaiwae oliv…® umbwaumwba lemoyo th…® mbuthuwe.   
\p
\v 102  \k Omega\k* \it [English: omega]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Vak 1:8; 21:6; 22:13). Hu thuwe \bd Alepa\bd*.   
\p
\v 103  \k Oniks\k* \it [English: onyx]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Vat 4:3; 21:11, 18-19). Oniks iye var…® thovuye lagh…®ye, na ma lemoyo inanjiwe. Hu thuwe \bd Var…® thovuthovuye na modanji lagh…®ye\bd*.   
\p
\v 104  \k Pailat\k* \it [English: Pilate]\it* ‚ÄĒ Pailat va Rom lenji gawana Judiya e t…®ne mbaŇča Jisas i vavagharewe. Iye i vatomwe weŇčgiya Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye lenji randeviva mbaŇča nuwanjiya amalagh…®niye iŇča na th…® rokros Jisas.   
\p
\v 105  \k Paradais\k* \it [English: Paradise]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Luk 23:43; 2Kor 12:4; Vat 2:7). Utuke iyake gharumwaru e vaŇča Grik ‚Äúuma thovuye moli.‚ÄĚ MbaŇča vavana th…® uno utuke iyake mbaŇča th…® utuŇča ghembako thovuye iyako Iden e t…®ne, iyaŇčganiye Loi i woraweŇčgiya Adam na Ive e yambaneke me r…®gheko. Buk Boboma Togha e t…®ne, paradais gharumwaru buruburu, ghembako thovuye iye raloŇčweloŇčweghath…® weya Jisas Krais th…® ru mare e ghereiye.   
\p
\v 106  \k Parisi\k* \it [English: Pharisee]\it* ‚ÄĒ Parisi va wabwi lagh…®ye moli regha i tomethi Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye e t…®nenji Jisas va ghambaŇča e t…®ne. Va th…® wabwi na regha weinjiyaŇčgiya mbaro gharavavaghareŇčgi. Parisi va th…® ghareghare mbaroke wolagh…®ye Loi va i giyakewe Mosese, na th…® vavagharena ghar…®ghar…® mbala th…® ghambuvakathaŇčgi. Tembe th…® vavaghareva thanavu na mbaro lemoyo iya th…® vatabo weiye Mosese le Mbaro. Thiye th…® nemo kaiwae th…® loŇčweghath…® lenji thovuye i kivalaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye lenji thovuye. MbaŇča vavana th…® varevare ŇčgoraŇčgiva ghar…®ghar…® th…® thovuye othembe lenji rerenuwaŇča raraithar…®. Parisi th…® th…®gh…®yawana Jisas na th…® vona ghae. Hu thuwe \bd Sadusi\bd*.   
\p
\v 107  \k Pentikos\k* \it [English: Pentecost]\it* ‚ÄĒ Hu thuwe \bd Pentekos gha Thaga\bd*, \bd Thaga\bd* e t…®ne.   
\p
\v 108  \k Pero\k* \it [English: Pharaoh]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Vak 7:10,13,21; Rom 9:17; Hib 11:24). Pero va Ijipt lenji kiŇč regha na regha idae.   
\p
\v 109  \k Ravamoru\k* \it [English: Savior]\it* ‚ÄĒ Jisas th…® uno idae Ravamoru kaiwae i vugha kamwath…® na ghar…®ghar…® val…®kaiwae ma th…® vaidi lenji thar…® ghalith…®we. Kaiwae lenji thar…®ko kaiwae ghar…®ghar…® ghanjilith…® mare na th…® meghaghath…® weya Loi. MbaŇča Jisas va i mare, i wo lith…®ke iyake othembe iye ghamberegha ma i vakathamun thar…®. Va i mare iyemaeŇčge thar…® gharavakatha ma i mare. Iya kaiwae Loi i numoten…®Ňčgiya thavala th…® loŇčweghath…® Jisas Krais; i wovarumwarumwaruŇčaŇčgi Jisas kaiwae. Jisas e le mare t…®ne tembe i vamoruŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® Seitan le vur…®gheghe e t…®ne.   
\p
\v 110  \k Ravavaghare\k* \it [English: Rabbai, Raboni, teacher]\it* ‚ÄĒ Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® dage weŇčgiya amaamala th…® thimba na idanji i lagh…®ye, th…®Ňča ‚ÄúRavavaghare.‚ÄĚ Va th…® vakatha iyake na i vatomwe th…® yavatata wanaŇčgi. VaŇča Hibru va th…®Ňča ‚ÄúRabai‚ÄĚ or ‚ÄúRaboni.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 111  \k Ravowovowo\k* \it [English: priest]\it* ‚ÄĒ Ravowovowo va amaamala gh…®mogh…®moru th…® tuthi na th…® vowo weya Loi Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye kaiwanji. Th…® vakatha vowo Ňägolo Boboma e t…®ne Jerusalem. Ravowovowo th…® tuthi Eron le bodaboda e t…®ne, iya kaiwae thiye Livai orumburumbuyeŇčgi. Hu thuwe Eron na Livai.  
\pi1 Ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye ‚Äúhigh priests‚ÄĚ lenji randeviva ‚ÄúChief Priest‚ÄĚ iye i lagh…®ye moli i kivwalaŇčgiya ravowovowoko wolagh…®ye. Mbe iye eŇčge Loi i vatomwe na i ru Woluwolu Boboma Moli ina Ňägolo Boboma e t…®ne moli. Gheko va i vowo weya Loi iye le thar…® na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva ghar…®ghar…® lenji thar…®.  
\pi1 Ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye lenji randeviva na thiye va ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye lenji randeviva, th…® uno Ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye lenji randeviva. Tembe th…® unova iyake ghar…®ghar…® vavana idanji i lagh…®ye th…® mena ravowovowo ghanjiuu kaiwanji.   
\p
\v 112  \k Rebeka\k* \it [English: Rebecca]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Rom 9:10-13). Rebeka va Eibrahan nariye Aisake levo. Iye va i ghamb…® gamwaruworuwo Iso na Jeikob. Hu thuwe \bd Eibraham\bd*, \bd Iso\bd* na \bd Jeikob\bd*.   
\p
\v 113  \k Reihab\k* \it [English: Rahab]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Hib 11:31; Jem 2:25). Va i vivako Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® vivatha na th…® ru vanautumako iya Loi va i dageraweko weŇčgi. MbaŇčaniye th…® variye gh…®mogh…®moru vavana th…® ru thuwole vanautumako na th…® kelakela mbala th…® ghareghare ŇčgoroŇčga ne th…® kivwalaŇčgi. Yathima wevoniye idae Reihab va i thalavuŇčgi na th…® kubaro e le Ňčgolo t…®ne. Va i vakatha iyake kaiwae i loŇčweghath…®kai Loi na i ghareghare Loi le renuwaŇča Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® kivwala vanautumako iyako. Muyai Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye va th…® mena na th…® kivwalaŇčgi vanautumako iyako. Va th…® tagavamareŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye e ghembako t…®ne mbe Reihab eŇčge. Iye na le bodaboda ma th…® tagavamareŇčgi kaiwae le thalavu weŇčgiya Loi le ghar…®ghar…®. Reihab iye i mboromboro weiye lolo regha Mat 1:5 i utuŇča iye Jisas rumbuye regha.   
\p
\v 114  \k Reitiyel\k* \it [English: Rachel]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Mat 2:18). Reitiyel va Jeikob levo eunda. Jeikob va i gharethovu lagh…®ye moli. Iye Josep na Benjamin t…®nanji. Mat 2:18 e t…®ne, Reitiyel idae i meth…® ot…®nat…®nae inanji Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye e t…®ne. Hu thuwe \bd Jeikob\bd*.   
\p
\v 115  \k Rom\k* \it [English: Rome]\it* ‚ÄĒ Rom iye ghemba lagh…®ye moli ina vanautuma regha idae Itali. MbaŇča Jisas va ina e yambaneke, Rom ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® kivwalaŇčgiya yambaneke le val…®vaŇčga lemoyo. Tembe Ňčgoreiyeva th…® kivwala Isirel. Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye va th…® botewoyathuŇčgi na thoŇčgo val…®kaiwanji th…® vakatha th…® wareri Isirel. Rom le randeviva lagh…®ye moli idae Sisa. Iye va kiŇč iye idae i lagh…®ye moli yambaneke lagh…®ye e t…®ne.   
\p
\v 116  \k Sabat\k* \it [English: Sabbath]\it* ‚ÄĒ Sabat iye towo ghambaŇča. Buk Boboma Teuye ghabuk idae R…®ghenda, va th…® rori Loi i kaiwo mbaŇča mbaŇčawona na i vakatha yambaneke, amba mbaŇča mbaŇčapir…®niye i towo kaiwae le kaiwoko iko. Loi va iŇča ghar…®gar…® val…®kaiwae th…® kaiwo mbaŇča mbaŇčawona, na mbaŇčapir…®niye e t…®ne th…® towo na th…® kururu weya amalagh…®niye.  
\pi1 Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye e lenji mbaro lemoyo Sabat kaiwae. Th…®Ňča ghar…®ghar…® ma val…®kaiwae th…® ndekaiwomun mbaŇčake iyake, na thoŇčgo th…® kaiwo th…® gharegaith…® wanaŇčgi. Iyake kaiwae th…® gharegaith…® mbaŇča Jisas i vamoru ghambweghambwera regha Sabat e t…®ne, na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva mbaŇča Jisas gharaghambu th…® vugha wit uneune na th…® ghan Sabat e t…®ne. Va th…®Ňča thiye th…® kaiwo.   
\p
\v 117  \k Sainai\k* \it [English: Sinai]\it* ‚ÄĒ Sainai iye ou iya Mosese va ve vorowe na i lavolevole Loi gheko na Loi i giya mbaro theyaworomawe. Hu thuwe Rom Ghaghambambaro ghamap. Hu thuwe \bd Mosese\bd*.   
\p
\v 118  \k Saiyon\k* \it [English: Zion]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Mat 13:33; 16:12; 1Kor 5:6-8; Gal 5:9; na vavana). Saiyon iye bobokulu regha ghemba Jerusalem ina e vwatanji. MbaŇča vavana Saiyon i meth…® Jerusalem lagh…®ye, na mbaŇča vavana i meth…® buruburu, Loi le ghamba yaku (Hib 12:22; Vat 14:1).   
\p
\v 119  \k Salpa\k* \it [English: sulfur]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Luk 17:29; Vat 9:17-18; 14:10; 19:20; 20:10; 21:8). Salpa iye var…® regha na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva vugha iya i ra weiye nd…®ghe une i mb…®le lagh…®ye na munduwae butiye i vur…®gheghe na i nda mbothinji. Va th…® vakaiwoŇča na th…® vakatha ‚Äúgunpowder.‚ÄĚ Ida regha ‚Äúbrimstone.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 120  \k Sam\k* \it [English: Psalms]\it* ‚ÄĒ Sam iye buk regha ina Buk Boboma Teuye. Wothu tarawa weya Loi inanji e t…®ne. KiŇč Deivid va i rori wothuke thiyake lemoyo moli.   
\p
\v 121  \k Sameriya\k* \it [English: Samaria]\it* ‚ÄĒ Sameriya le val…®vaŇčga iye provins lagh…®ye regha. Hu thuwe Jiu Thivathivaniye Jisas E GhambaŇča T…®ne ghamap. Ina Judiya na Galili e ghanji lughawoghawo. Jisas ghambaŇča e t…®ne, Sameriya ghar…®ghar…®niye ma Jiu moli kaiwae va i vivako rakakaiwoko th…® mena vanautuma vavanako th…® mban…®ruwoŇčgi na Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niyeko va inanjiko gheko th…® ghe weinjiyaŇčgi na th…® kururu weŇčgiya lenji loiŇčgi. Jiu inanji Judiya th…® botewoyathuŇčgiya Sameriya. Hu thuwe \bd Judiya\bd*.   
\p
\v 122  \k Samson\k* \it [English: Samson]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Hib 11:32). Samson iye va randeviva regha Jiu weŇčgia mbaŇča molao. Iye va lolo vur…®gheghe regha (mbunima na madibe) iye Loi va i wogiyawe.   
\p
\v 123  \k Samuwel\k* \it [English: Samuel]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Vak 3:24; 13:20; Hib 11:32). Samuwel va Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu lagh…®ye regha. Iye va i varuvu Deivid Isirel le kiŇč. Iye ghar…®ghar…®ko lenji randeviva lagh…®ye.   
\p
\v 124  \k Sanhidren\k* \it [English: Sanhedrin]\it* ‚ÄĒ Hu thuwe \bd Jiu lenji kot lagh…®ye\bd*.   
\p
\v 125  \k Sapaya\k* \it [English: sapphire]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Vat 4:3; 21:11, 18-19). Sapaya iye var…® thovuye lagh…®ye, na ma lemoyo inanjiwe. Hu thuwe \bd Var…® thovuthovuye na modanji lagh…®ye\bd*.   
\p
\v 126  \k Seitan\k* \it [English: Satan]\it* ‚ÄĒ Seitan iye nyao raraithar…® ghanjigiya na iye Loi ghath…®gh…®ya. I kwan…®yaroŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® na i mando th…® vakatha thar…®. Iye i vanuwov…®r…® valaŇčaŇčgi ghar…®ghar…®ko thiye th…® lonweghath…® weya Jisas Krais, lenji thar…®ko wolagh…®ye va th…® vakathaŇčgi, mbala th…® renuwaŇča Loi mava i numoten…®Ňčgi. Seitan idae regha Devil na yambaneke ghagiya. Hu thuwe \bd Bil…®sabul\bd*.   
\p
\v 127  \k Sep…®tuwajin…®t\k* \it [English: Septuagint]\it* ‚ÄĒ Hibru ghar…®ghar…®niye lenji buk, iye Buk Boboma Teuye, va th…® rori e vaŇča Hibru. Amba muyai Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niyeko va th…® mban…®raŇčgi Isirel e to gaith…® kaiwae, veth…® yaku e vanautuma lemoyo. Orumburumbunji lemoyo th…® vaŇča Grik, ma th…® ghareghare vaŇča Hibru. MbaŇčako iyako vaŇča Grik iye ghal…®ghal…®Ňča lagh…®ye moli. Iyake kaiwae, ghar…®ghar…® th…® vaghagh…®le Hibru lenji Buk Boboma Teuye na vaŇča Grik. Buk…®ke iyake idae Sep…®tuwajin…®t. MbaŇča vavana Buk Boboma Togha ghararorori th…® vakaiwoŇča utuutuke th…® mena Sep…®tuwajin…®t. Iyake kaiwae lenji utuutuke ma mboromboro moli weŇčgiya utuutu th…® mena Hibru lenji Buk Boboma Teuye.   
\p
\v 128  \k Sera\k* \it [English: Serah]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Rom 4:19; 9:9; Hib 11:11; 1Pit 3:6). Sera iye Eibraham levo. Othembe va i kwame theghathegha lagh…®ye, i vaidiya Aisake mbaŇča vama i yalagh…®sar…®. Hu thuwe \bd Eibraham\bd*.   
\p
\v 129  \k Sinamon\k* \it [English: cinnamon]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Vat 18.13). Sinamon iye bigi butiye thovuye th…® vakatha e umbwa regha njimwae. Butiye seiwo i vur…®gheghe, va modae lagh…®ye moli. Va th…® basi weiye bunama mbala bunama butiye i thovuye. Bunamake iyake th…® vakaiwoŇča na th…® varuvuya ghar…®ghar…®. MbaŇča vavana th…® vakaiwoŇča mbaŇča th…® beku kaka.   
\p
\v 130  \k Sip\k* \it [English: sheep]\it* ‚ÄĒ Ghar…®ghar…® th…® njimbukikiya sip yambaneke e le val…®vaŇčga vavana. Ko iyemaeŇčge ghar…®ghar…® lenji sip ghanjimbukiki mbaŇčaviye i tomethi weya Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye va th…® njimbukiki Buk Boboma e ghambaŇča t…®ne. Ghar…®ghar…®ko e lenji sip th…® njimbukiki sip ighanagha moli. Amalako i njimbukikiya sip idae sip gharanjimbunjimbu. MbaŇča vavana sip gharanjimbujimbu i njimbukikiya amalagh…®niye e le sip, na mbaŇča vavana ne i kaiwo weya amala e le sip. Sip ma mbaŇča wolagh…®ye inanji e ghemba, ko iyamaeŇčge sip gharanjimbujimbu ne i viva weŇčgi na th…® wa weya ghamba ghan…®Ňčga. Gharanjimunjimbu i yaku weiyaŇčgiya sip na i ghareghare sip regha na regha. Gharanjimbunjimbu ne i vivath lenji ghamba ghena weiye gana i megh…®liŇča na i mban…®ruwoŇčgi gougou. Gheko mane th…® vaidiya thar…®. Gharanjimbunjimbu va i ghena e lenji ghamba ghena ghagana ghaeko na thava rakaiv…® i ru na i kaiv…® sip. Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye mbaŇčaviye th…® vakaiwoŇča sip lenji vowo weya Loi.  
\pi1 Buk Boboma e t…®ne, mbaŇčaviye sip thiye Ňčgoreiye Loi le ghar…®ghar…® ŇčgaliŇčgaliyanji. Buk Boboma Togha e t…®ne Jisas mbanga vavana th…® uno iye ‚ÄúLe ghar…®ghar…® gharanjimbunjimbu‚ÄĚ na thiye th…® loŇčweghath…® Jisas th…® uno ‚Äúlenji sip.‚ÄĚ Hu thuwe \bd Sip Nariye\bd*.   
\p
\v 131  \k Sisa\k* \it [English: Caesar]\it* ‚ÄĒ Sisa va idae th…® giya weŇčgiya Rom lenji kiŇč. Rom va i kivwalaŇčgiya vanautuma lemoyo. Amba Sisa i tabona lenji kiŇč. Rom lenji kiŇč regha na regha th…® giya idakewe.   
\p
\v 132  \k Sodoma\k* \it [English: Sodom]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Mat 10:15; 11:23-24; Luk 17:29; Vat 11:8; na vavana). Sodoma iye ghemba regha Lot na le bodaboda th…® yakuwe. Iye Gomora ghadidiye. Sodoma na Gomora ghar…®ghar…®niye vambe th…® vakatha vakatha raraithar…® lemoyo. Iyake kaiwae, Loi va i mukuwoŇčgi ghembako thiyako e nd…®ghe. Hu thuwe \bd Lot\bd*.   
\p
\v 133  \k Solomon\k* \it [English: Solomon]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Mat 1:6-7; 6:29; 12:42; Luk 11:31; 12:27; Vak 7:47). Solomon va Deivid nariye regha. Iye va Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye lenji kiŇč lagh…®ye. Va mbaŇča regha, gh…®n…®lolo e t…®ne Loi i menawe na i vaito thebebe nuwaiya i giyawe. Solomon va i naŇčgo thimba kaiwae mbala ne i mbaroŇča wagiyaweŇčgiya le ghar…®ghar…®. Solomon i tabona kiŇč iye le thimba i lagh…®ye moli. Loi tembe i giyava gogomwau lagh…®ye moliwe. Solomon iye va i vatad Ňägolo Boboma iviva, iyake Mevathavatha Ňägoloniye ghath…®th…®, iya Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye va th…® kururu Loi we. Ňägolo Boboma Solomon le vatavatad weiye var…®, var…® thovuye, na bigibigi lemoyo modanji lagh…®ye, na i thovuye moli.   
\p
\v 134  \k Takis gharamban\k* \it [English: tax collectors]\it* ‚ÄĒ Jisas ghambaŇča e t…®ne, takis gharamban th…® kaiwo Rom kaiwae. Thiye va Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye ko iyemaeŇčge th…® thalavu Rom na th…® vakatha ghar…®ghar…® th…® vamodo takis Rom ghanjiragagaith…®Ňčgi kaiwanji. Rom va th…® kivwalaŇčgiya Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye na th…® mbaroŇčaŇčgi e vur…®gheghe. Iya kaiwae ghar…®ghar…® va th…® botewoyathuŇčgi. Na bigi reghava, takis gharamban mbaŇčaviye th…® mban mani Rom nuwaiya na e vwataeva, na th…® vareghare ghanjimberegha kaiwanji.   
\p
\v 135  \k Thaga\k* \it [English: festivals, feasts]\it* ‚ÄĒ Jiu va th…® vakathaŇčgi thaga theghathegha regha na regha e t…®ne, th…® renuwaŇčakikiya Loi va ghare weŇčgi. Thaga thagalima th…® utuŇča Buk Boboma Togha e t…®ne. Hu thuweŇčgi e raberabeke:  
\li1 1. \k Bred Ma Weiye Is…®t Gha Thaga\k* \it [English: feast of the unleavened bread]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Mat 26:17; Mak 14:1, 12; Luk 22:1, 7; Vak 12:3; 20:6). Thagake iyake th…® vakatha Thaga ValaŇčani e ghereiye moli na i wo mbaŇčapir…®. MbaŇčake mbaŇčapir…® thiyake e t…®nenji Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® ghan bred ma weiye is…®t. E kamwath…®ke iyake t…®ne th…® renuwaŇčakiki ŇčgoroŇčga Jiu th…® voraŇčgi Ijipt, na lenji vo va i maya moli na ma val…®kaiwanji th…® vakatha bred weiye is…®t na th…® vwala amba muyai th…® vo.  
\li1 2. \k Pentikos gha Thaga\k* \it [English: feast of pentecost]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Vak 2:1; 20:16; 1Kor 16:8). ‚ÄúPentikos‚ÄĚ gharumwaru iyelima. Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® vakatha thagake iyake mbaŇčapir…® Thaga ValaŇčani va i rikowe ghereiye mbala th…® vawarariŇča wit ghauloulo manjala Mei e le ghambako. Va Pentikos iya Nyao Boboma iyava i nja weŇčgiya gharghar…® thiye th…® loŇčweghath…® Jisas Krais (Vak 2:1-4).  
\li1 3. \k Thaga Vabobomaniye\k* \it [English: feast of dedication, feast of lights]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Jon 10:22). E thagake iyake Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® renuwaŇčakikiya mbaŇčaniye Judas Makabiyas i vakatha Loi le Ňägolo Boboma i th…®nava. Va i vakatha iyake mbaŇča e ghereiye Loi ghath…®gh…®yaŇčgi va th…® ru Ňčgoloko iyako na th…® vambigh…®ya Loi e marae. Jiu tembe th…® unova thagake iyake, ‚ÄúHanaka‚ÄĚ o ‚ÄúThaga Manjamanjalaniye.‚ÄĚ  
\li1 4. \k Thaga ValaŇčani\k* \it [English: feast of the passover, Passover]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Mat 26:2,5, 18-19; na vavana). Thaga ValaŇčani iye thaga lagh…®ye moli weŇčgiya Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye. Idake gharumwaru ‚ÄúvalaŇčani.‚ÄĚ Thagake iyake e t…®ne Jiu th…® renuwaŇčakikiya mbaŇčaniye va th…® voraŇčgi Ijipt e t…®ne na thiye rakarakayathuŇčgi. Amba muyai th…® voraŇčgi, mbaŇčaniye Loi va i dage vur…®gheghe weŇčgiya Ijipt gharayakuyaku ne i variye le nyao thovuye na i un…®gh…® nariye vir…®viva e Ňčgoloko regha na regha Ijipt e t…®ne. Ko iyemaeŇčge i dage weŇčgiya Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye na th…® vaunu sip nariye madibaewe e lenji Ňčgoloko regha na regha ghath…®n…®mba e vwatae iya kaiwae mbaŇča nyao thovuye i thuwe madibe, ne i valaŇčaniya Ňčgoloko iyako na mane i un…®gh…® nariye ina gheko. ThoŇčgo Ňčgoloko gharayakuyaku th…® vakatha Ňčgoreiye, nyao thovuye i valaŇčaniya Ňčgoloko iyako. Va mbaŇčaniye na i menamenake noroke, Thaga ValaŇčani e t…®ne, Ňčgolo regha na regha e t…®ne Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye va th…® vivatha sip nariye na th…® ghan…®Ňčga na regha (Luk 22:7-8).  
\li1 5. \k YoŇčathowathowa gha Thaga\k* \it [English: feast of tents]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Jon 7:2). Thagake iyake e t…®ne th…® tatarawawe kaiwae va th…® uloulovao. Th…® vatad…® yaŇčathowathowa na th…® yaku e t…®nenji wiki regha. E kamwath…®ke iyake th…® renuwaŇčakiki orumburumbunji lenji yakuyaku yoŇčathowathowa mbaŇča th…® loŇčgaloŇčga theghathegha iyevar…® amba muyai th…® ru val…®vaŇčgako iya Loi va i dageraweko weŇčgi.   
\p
\v 136  \k Thar…®\k* \it [English: sin]\it* ‚ÄĒ MbaŇča lolo regha i raka Loi le mbaro regha, iye thar…®. ThoŇčgo mbaro nasiye o lagh…®ye ghar…®ghar…® e maranji, iye tembe thar…®va Loi e marae. (Rom 3:9-20; 6:23).   
\p
\v 137  \k Thiye ma Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye\k* \it [English: gentile]\it* ‚ÄĒ Thiye ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye ma Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye. Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® nemo lagh…®ye moli kaiwae thiye ghanjimberegha Loi le tututhi ghar…®ghar…®niye, na th…® botewoyathu thiye ma Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye.   
\p
\v 138  \k Th…®na\k* \it [English: clean]\it* ‚ÄĒ Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye lenji renuwaŇča e t…®ne, thoŇčgo Jiu ma i th…®na, ma th…® vatomwe na th…® kururu weinji e Ňägolo Boboma t…®ne o e lenji Ňčgolo kururu t…®ne. Ne i mbigh…® thoŇčgo i ghan ghan…®Ňčga vavana o othembe i v…®ghath…® bigibigi vavana. Ghan…®Ňčgake thiyake na bigibigike thiyake Loi i dageten weŇčgi. Lolo regha i ghambwera ghambwera vavana, Ňčgoreiye lepelo, o thoŇčgo i v…®ghath…® kaka, thiya th…® mbigh…®. Tembe Ňčgoreiyeva, ela i ghataŇča voruvoru o i ghamb…® ne i mbigh…®. ThoŇčgo lolo regha i mb…®gh…® Loi e marae, wo i wa weya ravowovowo na i vowo weya Loi amba muyai i th…®nava.   
\p
\v 139  \k Topas\k* \it [English: topaz]\it* ‚ÄĒ (Vat 4:3; 21:11, 18-19). Topas iye var…® thovuye lagh…®ye, na ma lemoyo inanjiwe. Hu thuwe \bd Var…® thovuthovuye na modanji lagh…®ye\bd*.   
\p
\v 140  \k Toto Thovuye\k* \it [English: Good News]\it* ‚ÄĒ Loi le utu weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye th…® uno Toto Thovuye. Le utuke iyake: Loi va i variye Nariye, Jisas Krais, na i njama yambaneke na mbala i vamoruŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® na ma th…® vaidiya lenji thar…® ghalith…®, na i vakatha kamwath…® na th…® tabona Loi le ŇčgamaŇčgama.   
\p
\v 141  \k UturaŇčgiya thar…® na roiteteŇčgi\k* \it [English: repent]\it* ‚ÄĒ MbaŇča lolo regha i ghareghare i vakatha thar…®, ko iyemaeŇčge nuwaiya i ghambu Loi le renuwaŇča, ne i uturaŇčgiya le thar…® na i roiteteŇčgi. Amba Loi i numoten…®ngi le thar…®.   
\p
\v 142  \k ValaŇčani\k* \it [English: Passover]\it* ‚ÄĒ Hu thuwe \bd Thaga ValaŇčani\bd*, \bd Thagathaga\bd* e t…®ne.   
\p
\v 143  \k Var…® thovuthovuye na modanji lagh…®ye\k* \it [English: precious stones, jewels]\it* ‚ÄĒ Vatomwe 21 e t…®ne, Jon va i utuŇča Ghemba Boboma iyava i thuwe ghavatomwe e t…®ne. Ghembako ghagana ghambagh…®mbagh…® th…® vakatha weiye tomethi var…® var…®yaworo na variwo. Thiye ghanjiyamoyamo i thovuye moli, th…® ndalandala na lenji kala mbe tomethi. Var…®ko var…®yaworo na variwo thiyake:  
\li1 1. jaspa \it [English: jasper]\it* ‚ÄĒ vwivu o maŇčemaŇče  
\li1 2. sapaya \it [English: sapphire]\it* ‚ÄĒ Ňčgoreiye buruburu (blu)  
\li1 3. ageit \it [English: agate]\it* ‚ÄĒ (th…® uno ida NIV e t…®ne, kalsidoni): tomethi kala, Ňčgoreiye kakaleva na braun  
\li1 4. emerold \it [English: emerald]\it* ‚ÄĒ vwivu lagh…®ye  
