\p
\v 144  \k Vowo\k* \it [English: sacrifice]\it* ‚ÄĒ Buk Boboma Teuye ghambaŇča e t…®ne, Loi va i vatomwe weŇčgiya le ghar…®ghar…® mbala th…® vowowe. Vowo mbe tomethi. Vowo regha iya mbala Loi ne i numotena lolo regha le thar…®. Loloko i vakatha thar…®ko iye val…®kaiwae Loi i botewo. Thar…® ghalith…®we i mare. Amba muyai Jisas le mena, Loi le ghar…®ghar…® ne th…® womena thetheghan e Ňägolo Boboma na thetheghan…®ko iyako ne i mare kaiwanji. Ghar…®ghar…®ko ghanjimberegha ma th…® tagavamare thetheghan. Va th…® giya thetheghan weŇčgiya ravowovowo na th…® tagavamareŇčgi ghar…®ghar…® kaiwanji. Thetheghanko th…® vowoko va Ňčgoreiye burumwaka gh…®moru, sip o gout, thiye thovuthovuye vara. Mava thar…® ina weŇčgi. Ghar…®ghar…®ko mbaŇčaviye th…® vakatha vowo vavana na th…® vata agowe kaiwae ghare weŇčgi.   
\p
\v 145  \k Waen une\k* \it [English: Grape]\it* ‚ÄĒ Waen une th…® thovuye. Waen une ŇčgaliŇčgaliyae ina page ###‚Äď### e lughawoghawo. Waen une th…® mbuthu e umbwa, ma iye umbwa moli. Iye ngoreiye thiyo. Th…® vakaiwoŇča une na th…® vakatha waen th…® mun. Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye va th…® kabu waen thiyo lemoyo e lenji uma na th…® njimbukiki wagiyawe mbala th…® rau na une ighanagha. Waen ghauma ŇčgaliŇčgaliya in page ###‚Äď### e lughawoghawo.   